Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2025 Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300. Boasting a sleek black exterior and a well-appointed interior, this vehicle is a true testament to Mercedes-Benz's commitment to excellence.

Highlighted features include:
• Panoramic sunroof
• Backup camera
• Heated and ventilated front seats
• Blind spot monitoring
• Advanced USB package

Step inside and you'll be surrounded by premium amenities, such as dual-zone automatic climate control, a premium audio system, and a 11.9" center touchscreen display. The turbocharged 2.0L I4 engine and 9-speed automatic transmission deliver a dynamic and efficient driving experience, with an impressive 25 city/35 highway MPG.

This C 300 also comes equipped with a host of advanced safety features, including forward collision warning, automatic emergency braking, and a rearview camera. The Mercedes-Benz brand is synonymous with unparalleled craftsmanship and engineering, and this vehicle upholds that reputation.

As a certified pre-owned Mercedes-Benz, this C-Class has undergone a rigorous inspection and reconditioning process, ensuring it meets the highest standards of quality and reliability. You can drive with confidence, knowing that this vehicle has been meticulously cared for and is backed by the Mercedes-Benz name.

Discover the true essence of luxury and performance with this 2025 Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the exceptional value and driving dynamics this vehicle has to offer.

Unleash your adventurous spirit with the 2020 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 Custom Trail Boss, a powerhouse designed for those who demand more from their truck. Equipped with a robust EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine delivering an impressive 355 horsepower and 520 lb-ft of torque, this beast is ready to conquer any terrain. The advanced 4WD drivetrain ensures superior traction and control, whether you're navigating rugged trails or cruising through city streets. Paired with a smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission, every drive promises to be as exhilarating as it is comfortable.
The Silverado Custom Trail Boss stands out not just in performance but also in style and capability. Its bold design features aggressive styling cues that command attention wherever you go. Inside, you'll find a spacious cabin equipped with modern amenities tailored for comfort and convenience on long journeys or daily commutes alike. Ready to elevate your driving experience? Visit us today to test drive the Chevy Silverado Custom Trail Boss and feel the power firsthand! Don’t miss out on owning this exceptional blend of strength and sophistication—your ultimate adventure awaits!

With years of experience serving the area, our dealership is dedicated to offering high-quality, pre-owned vehicles to our customers.
We serve Denver, Lakewood, Littleton, Englewood, Centennial, Parker, Greenwood Village, Aurora, Arvada, Westminster, Thornton, Broomfield, Henderson, Commerce City, Colorado Springs, Boulder, Loveland, Longmont, Fort Collins, Greeley and everywhere in-between!

Our goal is for you to be so delighted with your vehicle purchase that you’ll come see us when you need your next car and will happily recommend us to friends and family. Customer referrals are the ultimate compliment.
With many vehicle shopping options available, we differentiate ourselves by understanding our local car-buying community and satisfying its needs, helping valued local customers like you, find the vehicle that’s the “right fit”.
Feel free to browse our inventory online and check out the Featured Vehicles section on our homepage. If you see a vehicle you like, submit an online quote request, or contact us to schedule a test drive.
To learn more about our dealership and how we can help with your next vehicle purchase, please call or stop by in person. We look forward to meeting you.

In either case, the manufacturer must file a public report describing the safety-related defect or noncompliance with a Federal motor vehicle safety standard, the involved vehicle/equipment population, the major events that resulted in the recall determination, a description of the remedy, and a schedule for the recall. NHTSA monitors each safety recall to ensure the manufacturers provide owners safe, free, and effective remedies according to the Safety Act and Federal regulations. Manufacturers are obligated to attempt to notify owners of recalled products. For vehicles, that means manufacturers merge their own records of vehicle purchasers with current state vehicle registration information. For equipment, where state registration records do not exist, manufacturers are obligated to notify their distribution chain and known purchasers of the recalled equipment. However, even if you do not receive a notification, if your vehicle, child restraint, or other item of equipment is involved in a safety recall, the manufacturer is obligated to provide a free remedy. Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Android Auto/Apple CarPlay smart device wireless mirroring
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Here's what sets us apart: Locally & Family Owned - Since 1967, our team has been proudly serving communities throughout Western North Carolina. INFO ABOUT THIS VEHICLE: Our Magnetic Gray Metallic 2017 Toyota Tacoma TRD Sport has 67,878 miles with Graphite w/Gun Metal interior color. Stock Number WU30087 Important Package Information Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.
  • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.

description:
Discover the versatile and well-equipped 2013 Chevrolet Equinox LS, a compact SUV that offers a smooth and capable performance. This Equinox boasts a 2.4L 4-Cylinder SIDI DOHC engine paired with a 6-Speed Automatic transmission and All-Wheel Drive, delivering an impressive fuel economy of 20 MPG in the city and 29 MPG on the highway.

• License Plate Bracket, Front

Beyond its efficient powertrain, this Equinox is packed with a range of desirable features that cater to your needs. The vehicle is finished in a sleek Silver exterior, complemented by a well-appointed interior with Cloth Seat Trim. Enjoy the convenience of features like Power Windows, Power Door Locks, Cruise Control, and Steering Wheel-Mounted Audio Controls.

For your entertainment and connectivity, the Equinox is equipped with a 6-Speaker Audio System, SiriusXM Satellite Radio, and an AM/FM Stereo with CD Player and MP3 Capability. Stay connected with the OnStar Directions & Connections system, providing emergency communication and navigation assistance.

Safety is a top priority, and the Equinox delivers with Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control to help keep you and your passengers secure. The 4-Wheel Disc Brakes with ABS and the Traction Control System further enhance the vehicle's handling and stability.

Designed with versatility in mind, the Equinox offers a Split Folding Rear Seat, allowing you to easily accommodate your cargo and passenger needs. The 17-Inch Aluminum Wheels and Variably Intermittent Wipers add to the vehicle's stylish and functional appeal.

This well-equipped 2013 Chevrolet Equinox LS is an exceptional value, offering a compelling blend of performance, comfort, and convenience. Experience the Equinox for yourself and discover how it can enhance your driving experience. Visit our showroom today to take a closer look and schedule a test drive.

PLEASE HURRY!!! WILL NOT LAST LONG!!!How does the Yukon drive? The Yukon Denali, which is what we tested, is the only model in the lineup that comes standard with a 6.2-liter V8. The engine produces gobs of power, and the Denali's 6.6-second sprint to 60 mph is among the segment's quickest. The 10-speed automatic transmission, though smooth and pleasant enough in everyday driving, takes a few beats to shift into a lower gear when you put your foot down. We also noticed that the transmission treats pushes of manual gear selector buttons more like suggestions than commands.The Yukon's substantial weight and top-heavy design sabotage any chance of praiseworthy handling. It's something you have to accept with a vehicle this large. On the upside, the brakes make it easy to stop smoothly, and the light steering effort is perfect for navigating a crowded Costco lot. The Denali isn't as capable off-road as the AT4 trim, but its air suspension and two-speed transfer case will get you out of some tough spots.How does the Yukon drive? The Denali isn't as capable off-road as the AT4 trim, but its air suspension and two-speed transfer case will get you out of some tough spots.

Discover the exceptional 2024 Honda Prologue Touring, a cutting-edge electric vehicle that redefines the driving experience. With its striking blue exterior, this Prologue Touring model offers a seamless blend of style, technology, and performance that is sure to captivate your senses.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this Prologue Touring is tailored to meet your every need. Key highlights include:

• Non-Smoker Vehicle
• 4 New Tires Installed
• Clean CARFAX
• One-Owner Vehicle
• Google Android Auto™
• Apple CarPlay®
• Bluetooth Hands-Free Connectivity
• Navigation System with Turn-by-Turn Guidance
• Backup Camera
• Power Locks and Windows

Elevating your driving experience, the Prologue Touring is equipped with a powerful electric powertrain that delivers 212 horsepower and an exceptional 107 MPGe in the city and 91 MPGe on the highway. Paired with a smooth 1-speed automatic transmission and front-wheel drive, this electric marvel offers a responsive and efficient ride that will leave you in awe.

Slip into the luxurious cabin and be enveloped by the Bose Premium Audio System, 12 speakers, and the intuitive touchscreen display that seamlessly integrates your smartphone. Enjoy the comfort of heated front seats, a power driver's seat, and dual-zone automatic climate control, all while taking in the panoramic view through the power moonroof.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and the Prologue Touring delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance features. From the Lane Keeping Assist System and Collision Mitigation Braking System to the Blind Spot Information System and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, you can drive with confidence knowing that your safety is a top priority.

This one-owner, non-smoker Prologue Touring is a true gem, and with 4 new tires recently installed, it's ready to take you on your next adventure. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the future of electric driving. Schedule a test drive today and discover the exceptional 2024 Honda Prologue Touring.

Experience the pinnacle of luxury and performance with this exceptional 2024 INFINITI QX80 LUXE. This stunning SUV boasts a commanding presence on the road, blending sophisticated style with uncompromising capability.

• Navigation system: INFINITI InTouch Navigation
• Google Android Auto™

• Keyless Entry

Powered by a robust 5.6L V8 engine and equipped with 4-wheel drive, this QX80 LUXE delivers exceptional performance and confidence in any driving condition. With an impressive 13 city/19 highway MPG, it balances power and efficiency to meet your everyday needs.

The meticulously crafted interior of the QX80 LUXE surrounds you in unparalleled luxury. Sink into the plush, leather-appointed seats and enjoy the convenience of heated and cooled functionality. The panoramic sunroof floods the cabin with natural light, creating a truly open and airy atmosphere.

Cutting-edge technology is at your fingertips, thanks to the INFINITI InTouch Navigation system. Stay connected and in control with seamless integration of your smartphone via Apple CarPlay® and Android Auto™. The premium Bose audio system with 13 speakers delivers an immersive listening experience, ensuring every journey is a pleasure for the senses.

Safety is paramount in the QX80 LUXE, with a suite of advanced driver-assistance features, including Automatic Emergency Braking, Blind Spot Monitoring, and Adaptive Cruise Control. These intelligent systems work tirelessly to help protect you and your loved ones on the road.

This one-owner QX80 LUXE with a clean CARFAX report is a rare find. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the pinnacle of luxury and capability. Schedule a test drive today and discover the exceptional value this vehicle has to offer.

With an impressive 54 MPG city and 50 MPG highway, you'll not only save at the pump but also reduce your carbon footprint. Our knowledgeable sales team is ready to answer any questions you may have and guide you through the purchasing process. ONE OWNER | LOW MILES | HIGH COUNTRY LUXURY | BEST VALUE IN THE MARKET

This 2024 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 High Country in rich Dark Ash Metallic isnt just a pickup, its a rolling executive suite with a work ethic. Built for drivers who want premium comfort without sacrificing real truck capability, this High Country blends chrome-trimmed confidence with serious 4WD muscle.

Underneath the polished exterior sits a 10-speed automatic transmission and a rugged 4WD system, ready for job sites, boat ramps, or weekend escapes. Inside, youll find a cabin that feels more like a luxury SUV than a traditional pickup.

High Country Highlights

10-Way Power Driver & Passenger Seats with Lumbar

Ventilated & Heated Front Seats

Heated Second-Row Outboard Seats

12.3" Multicolor Digital Driver Display

HD Surround Vision & Bed View Camera

Adaptive Cruise Control

Power Tailgate & Power Sliding Rear Window

Integrated Trailer Brake Controller

Trailer Side Blind Zone Alert

Chrome Assist Steps & Chrome Recovery Hooks

Chevytec Spray-On Bedliner

High Capacity Suspension Package

Preferred Equipment Group 3LZ

From rain-sensing wipers to Wi-Fi hotspot capability and Safety Alert Seat, this High Country is packed with smart tech and upscale touches that make every drive feel first-class.

Clean, one-owner history and loaded with premium features, this Silverado delivers luxury, capability, and value in one bold package.

Available at Maher Chevrolet Pre-Owned Cars
2901 34th St N, St. Petersburg, FL

This well-equipped truck is the perfect blend of performance, technology, and style, making it an exceptional value in the pre-owned market. Visit our showroom today to take this remarkable vehicle for a test drive and discover why it's the perfect choice for your next adventure.

Whether for work or play, this Chevrolet Silverado 1500 is built to handle the job. In addition to being well-cared for, this Chevrolet Silverado 1500 has very low mileage making it a rare find. Just what you've been looking for. With quality in mind, this vehicle is the perfect addition to take home. More information about the 2016 Chevrolet Silverado 1500: The full-size pickup truck segment has never been more popular, or more competitive. With its 2016 Silverado 1500, Chevrolet has staked its claim once again as king of the hill. The 2016 Silverado boasts a refined level of comfort, sophistication and brute force not found in trucks from Ford and Ram, specifically in the all-aluminum range of engines, where Chevy has laid claim to the most fuel-efficient V8 found in a full-size truck. In fact, at 23 mpg on the highway, the 5.3L unit provides a better return than the turbocharged V6 employed in the Ford F-150. Add in the fact that Chevy managed to make so many innovative changes while keeping the base price steady, and it's no surprise that the Silverado is a hit. description: Get ready to hit the road in style with this sleek Silver 2018 Chevrolet Equinox! With its 1.5L Turbo DOHC 4-cylinder engine under the hood, this beauty is ready to roar to life with 170 horsepower and 203 lb-ft of torque at your command. Navigate through any terrain with ease thanks to the all-wheel drive capability and smooth suspension system. Whether you're cruising down the highway or taking a scenic route off the beaten path, the Equinox has your back with its reliable performance.The exterior features a striking design with bright lower window trim, high intensity discharge headlamps, and body-color accents for a modern look. The interior is just as impressive with a comfortable and spacious layout, including a rear split-folding seat for extra cargo space when needed.Stay connected and entertained on the go with the 6-speaker audio system, steering wheel controls, and keyless start functionality. The active noise cancellation system ensures a quiet ride, while the rear vision camera gives you added peace of mind when reversing.Safety is a top priority with dual-stage airbags, stability control, and a rear child security lock system. The Teen Driver mode allows you to set customizable vehicle settings to encourage safe driving habits for new drivers. Plus, the Tire Pressure Monitor with Tire Fill Alert keeps you informed about your tire health on the road.This Chevrolet Equinox also comes with a Carfax report, so you can purchase with confidence knowing the vehicle's history. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a reliable and stylish SUV that's ready for all your adventures. Get behind the wheel of this 2018 Equinox and experience the thrill of the open road! Visit Quality Value Auto Sales online at www.qualityvalueautosales.com to see more pictures of this vehicle as well as a walk-around video. You can also give us a call at 918-251-8181 today! This Corvette Stingray 1LT is powered by the legendary 6.2L V8 paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission with paddle shifters, delivering true rear-wheel-drive performance. Standout features include Chevrolet MyLink with built-in navigation, Bose premium audio system, performance exhaust, magnetic selective ride control, head-up display, rear backup camera, remote start, dual-zone automatic climate control, leather interior, heated and ventilated front seats, power driver and passenger seats, keyless entry and push-button start, HID headlights, limited-slip rear differential, and a 1-piece removable roof panel for open-air driving.

The Stingray delivers a balance of everyday usability and true sports-car performance, making it one of the most iconic American performance cars ever built.

Every pre-owned vehicle at U-J Chevrolet undergoes a comprehensive multi-point inspection and factory-level reconditioning process performed by certified technicians before being offered for sale.

description: This is a no-excuses 2013 Ford Mustang GT Premium finished in eye-popping Gotta Have It Green Metallic Tri-Coat with a Charcoal Black interior — a low-mileage, one-owner example that drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Under the hood sits the legendary 5.0L Coyote V8, producing a furious 412 hp and 390 ft.-lbs. of torque. This is raw, analog muscle with modern poise — efficient for its class too, rated at 15 MPG city and 26 MPG highway, and with under 16,000 miles (averaging less than 2,000 miles per year) this Mustang is practically brand new. Factory-equipped features (Premium trim) include: - Powertrain & Performance - 5.0L V8 engine delivering 412 hp and 390 ft.-lbs. of torque. - Sport-tuned suspension and chassis calibration engineered for sharp handling and confident cornering. - Dual exhaust with aggressive sound and performance tuning. - Electronic stability control, traction control and ABS for controlled, capable performance. - Interior Comfort & Convenience - Leather-trimmed, bolstered front sport seats for supportive seating during spirited driving. - Power-adjustable driver’s seat for personalized comfort. - Dual-zone automatic climate control to keep driver and passenger comfortable. - Tilt and telescoping steering column, steering-wheel-mounted audio and cruise controls. - Audio, Connectivity & Electronics - Ford SYNC voice-activated communications and media system for hands-free calling and audio control. - Premium Shaker audio system (factory premium sound) with enhanced speakers and bass for a fuller listening experience. - Auxiliary/USB inputs and iPod integration for easy media connectivity. - Bluetooth hands-free phone connectivity. - Exterior & Styling - Striking Gotta Have It Green Metallic Tri-Coat factory paint — a head-turning, signature Mustang color. - Charcoal Black interior trim that complements the aggressive exterior. - Distinctive Mustang styling cues: sculpted hood, bold grille, and iconic tri-bar taillamps. - Fog lamps and sporty alloy wheels (factory fitment) for a complete performance look. - Safety & Security - Front, side and curtain airbags for comprehensive occupant protection. - Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS). - Remote keyless entry and factory immobilizer for secure operation. - Built-in stability and traction systems to help keep power in check. This Mustang comes with a clean CARFAX and a single owner — no accidents, no drama. Condition is excellent inside and out, mechanical and cosmetic condition match the mileage. If you want brute-force V8 performance wrapped in classic Mustang attitude, this GT Premium is exactly what you need. Don’t hesitate — cars like this don’t stay on the lot. Schedule a test drive today and feel the 5.0L roar for yourself. We take trades and ship vehicles nationwide. Visit our website for 60 detailed photos. Elevate your driving experience with the 2025 Subaru Forester Premium. This exceptional SUV combines style, capability, and cutting-edge technology, making it the perfect companion for your adventures.

• VISION HYUNDAI OF WEBSTER

Boasting a spacious and well-appointed interior, the Forester Premium offers the perfect blend of comfort and versatility. Enjoy the panoramic moonroof, which floods the cabin with natural light, and the premium textured cloth upholstery that provides a touch of elegance. The heated front seats and dual-zone automatic climate control ensure you and your passengers stay cozy, no matter the weather.

Under the hood, the 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V engine, paired with the Lineartronic CVT and Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, delivers a smooth and confident driving experience. With an impressive 26 city/33 highway MPG, this Forester Premium is both powerful and efficient, making it the perfect choice for your daily commute and weekend adventures.

The Subaru Forester Premium is equipped with a wealth of advanced safety features, including Subaru's EyeSight Driver Assist Technology, Blind Spot Detection, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert. These cutting-edge systems work together to help keep you and your loved ones secure on the road.

Connectivity is also a top priority in the 2025 Forester Premium, with the Subaru 11.6" Multimedia Plus System providing seamless integration of your smartphone, navigation, and entertainment needs. Stay connected and entertained throughout your journey.

With its impressive capabilities, premium features, and unwavering safety, the 2025 Subaru Forester Premium is the perfect SUV to elevate your driving experience. Visit us today and let us show you why this exceptional vehicle should be your next automotive companion.

Original MSRP: $105,055
Experience exhilarating performance and unmistakable style in this 2022 Mercedes-Benz GLE 53 AMG 4MATIC, a single-owner SUV originally delivered by Mercedes-Benz of North Olmsted. With just 44,487 miles, this GLE 53 is equipped with a stunning blend of AMG power, luxury refinement, and cutting-edge technology. Finished in MANUFAKTUR Diamond White Metallic over AMG Classic Red/Black Exclusive Nappa Leather, it offers an arresting visual presence matched by its 429-hp AMG-enhanced 3.0L inline-6 turbo with EQ Boost.

This vehicle boasts an exceptionally high level of factory equipment, with a $105,055 original MSRP and desirable premium packages. Recent dealership servicing (January 2026) includes new tires, front brakes and rotors, brake fluid flush, alignment, and full fluid service ensuring its turn-key ready for its next owner.
**Highlighted Features and Packages:** - **Driver Assistance Package** Active Distance Assist DISTRONIC, Active Steering Assist, and Route-Based Speed Adaptation - **AMG Night Package** Gloss black exterior accents for a stealthy aesthetic - **Parking Assistance Package** Surround View Camera and Active Parking Assist - **Burmester High-End 3D Surround Sound System** Concert-level clarity with rich acoustic detail - **Multicontour Front Seats w/Massage** Active bolstering and massage programs for driver and passenger - **Warmth & Comfort Package** Heated front armrests, rapid-heating front seats, and more - **Soft-Close Doors** Quiet, refined closure at every touch - **Head-Up Display** AMG-specific performance data projected on the windshield - **22" Matte Black AMG Cross-Spoke Forged Wheels** Paired with High-Performance Tires for confident handling - **AMG Performance Exhaust System** Signature AMG sound with adjustable modes - **Heated Rear Seats, Heated Washer System, Trailer Hitch** Added utility and winter comfort - **AMG Carbon Fiber Trim** Sporty interior ambiance with genuine carbon-fiber detailing
Ownership & Service History:
- 1-owner, corporate vehicle driven approx. 11,386 miles/year (below average for its class)
- Originally in service February 2022, still under factory warranty coverage until approx. March 2026 or 50,000 miles (verify with dealer)
- Extensive dealer maintenance history, including recent major service and tire/brake replacement
When new, this GLE 53 retailed for $105,055. A comparably equipped 2024 GLE 53 now exceeds $112,000, offering you tremendous value in this well-maintained example with tasteful factory upgrades.

We specialize in out-of-town and out-of-state sales, delivering luxury nationwide with the same award-winning service our local clients trust. Discover why were a Top-Rated Dealer and a go-to destination for exceptional Mercedes-Benz vehicles.

Experience the power and efficiency of this 2023 Jeep Grand Cherokee 4xe Trailhawk, a rugged 4WD plug-in hybrid (L4, 2.0L PHEV) built for adventure and daily driving. Located in Muskogee, OK, this Trailhawk blends off-road capability with advanced hybrid performance, delivering impressive fuel savings without sacrificing torque or trail-ready features. This Jeep Grand Cherokee 4xe is competitively priced — the best price available — making it an exceptional value for buyers seeking performance, tech, and economy.

Inside, enjoy premium comforts including a heated steering wheel and a refined cabin designed for both long trips and city commutes. Safety and convenience come standard with adaptive cruise control and a back-up camera to make driving easier and more secure. Entertainment is handled by XM Radio and satellite radio, offering countless stations and programming for every taste. The Trailhawk trim brings enhanced suspension, protective skid plates, and aggressive styling cues for confident off-road performance while maintaining a smooth on-road ride.

This 2023 Jeep Grand Cherokee 4xe Trailhawk is ideal for environmentally conscious drivers who refuse to compromise capability. With cutting-edge hybrid technology, 4WD traction, and a comprehensive features list, it stands out in its class. Visit Muskogee, OK to see this exceptional plug-in hybrid for yourself — with the best price available, it won't last long. Schedule a test drive today and experience the blend of efficiency and adventure.

Additional Information
Price includes $2000 trade and $2000 finance discounts

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2023 Lexus GX 460. This premium SUV boasts a commanding presence on the road, combining exceptional performance, unparalleled luxury, and advanced technology to deliver a truly remarkable driving experience.

Packed with an impressive array of features, this GX 460 is equipped with:

• Premium Package
• Navigation system: Lexus Enform Dynamic Navigation
• Dual Front & Rear Auto Air Conditioner
• LED Front Fog & Driving Lamp
• Front & Rear Heated Seats
• NuLuxe Seat Trim
• Ventilated Front Seats
• Windshield Wiper Control w/Rain Sensor
• Windshield De-Icer

Powered by a robust 4.6L V8 DOHC Dual VVT-i 32V engine, this GX 460 delivers a smooth and responsive driving experience, effortlessly navigating both city streets and off-road terrain with its 4WD capabilities. With an impressive 19 MPG on the highway, you can enjoy the thrill of driving without compromising on fuel efficiency.

The striking black exterior exudes a bold and sophisticated presence, while the well-appointed interior offers a luxurious and comfortable cabin. Sink into the plush NuLuxe seats and let the ventilated front seats keep you cool, even on the hottest days. The Lexus Enform Dynamic Navigation system and 360° View Parking Camera provide seamless connectivity and enhanced visibility, ensuring a stress-free driving experience.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and this GX 460 is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Blind Spot Warning/Intervention, Lane Departure Warning/Prevention, and Pre-Collision Warning/Prevention. You can drive with confidence, knowing that you and your loved ones are well-protected.

Whether you're embarking on a family adventure or seeking a premium daily driver, this 2023 Lexus GX 460 is the perfect choice. Experience the pinnacle of luxury, performance, and technology by scheduling a test drive today.

Trusted Name for 60+ Years Serving our community for over six decades with integrity, quality, & customer satisfaction The Hansel Auto Group story begins in 1851. Joseph Hansel first entered the transportation industry selling horse-drawn carriages. Joseph's son continued to build the Hansel name, opening the family's first automotive dealership in 1901. Hansel Auto Group first expanded into the Sonoma Valley in 1961 under the leadership of Walter Hansel. Walter believed that the Hansel name was about more than just selling cars. We are committed to giving back to our community. Walter Hansel partnered with multiple other local business owners to found what would become the local chapter of United Way. This began a long tradition of community involvement by the Hansel family.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Powered by a robust 2.0L Turbocharged engine paired with a smooth 9-Speed Automatic transmission and All-Wheel Drive, this Evoque Dynamic delivers an exceptional driving experience. With an impressive EPA-estimated 20 MPG in the city and 27 MPG on the highway, you'll enjoy the perfect balance of power and efficiency.

Step inside and be captivated by the premium Grained Leather Seat Trim, the Meridian Sound System, and the state-of-the-art InControl Navigation Pro system. The Panoramic Moonroof floods the cabin with natural light, creating a spacious and airy atmosphere. Enjoy the convenience of the Power Liftgate, the Heated Front Seats, and the Auto High-beam Headlights, all designed to enhance your driving experience.

Safety is paramount, and this Evoque Dynamic delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Occupant Sensing Airbag, Rear Anti-Roll Bar, and Electronic Stability Control. The Exterior Parking Camera Rear and the Lane Departure Assist system provide added peace of mind on the road.

This exceptional 2026 Land Rover Range Rover Evoque Dynamic is a true testament to the brand's commitment to excellence. Experience the pinnacle of luxury and performance by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be captivated by this exceptional SUV.

It continues to be one of their top-selling vehicles, encouraging Ford to put their best foot forward with the 2017 model. The F-150 competes with the Ram, the Chevrolet Silverado and the GMC Sierra 1500, among others, in the full-sized truck category. Ford is clearly pushing its new technology and new ideas with the F-150, offering plenty of options not available anywhere else in this class, such as a 360-degree camera and integrated loading ramps stowed in the pickup bed. A smaller, more fuel efficient EcoBoost engine is also available, which should further improve fuel economy while providing the same kind of horsepower that would normally be delivered by mid-grade V8 engines. At the same time, the F-150 continues to excel at traditional truck tasks, with a best in class towing capacity of 12,200 pounds when properly equipped. description: Payne Brownsville Volkswagen is honored to present a wonderful example of pure vehicle design... this 2017 Honda Ridgeline RTL only has 89,668mi on it and could potentially be the vehicle of your dreams! This Honda Ridgeline RTL comes equipped with all wheel drive, which means no limitations as to how or where you can drive. Different terrains and varying weather conditions will have little effect as to how this vehicle performs. It's not a misprint. And the odometer isn't broken. This is a very low mileage Honda Ridgeline. A rare find these days. This White Honda is clean and shiny exterior makes it look like it came straight from the factory. While virtually every pickup truck in the U.S. uses a body on frame style chassis, the Honda Ridgeline utilizes a car-like unibody structure. This allows for a much more sophisticated driving experience, with a stiffer chassis, a better ride and much better handling, making it far more refined and makes fewer compromises than just about any truck on the market. The Honda Ridgeline competes with other compact pickup trucks such as the Toyota Tacoma. * Roomy interior, car-like driving experience, compact exterior dimensions, innovative truck bed with tons of storage options, available all-wheel drive. For more information about this vehicle call us at 956-517-1301!

                      Safety and Security
                      • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
                      • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.

description:
Vehicle Details
2020 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT 4WD — powerful performance meets comfort in Muskogee, OK. Equipped with a proven 5.3L V8 gasoline engine and four-wheel drive, this Chevrolet Silverado delivers confident towing, dependable highway cruising, and capable off-road traction. The LT trim adds convenience and technology for daily driving: steering wheel audio controls keep music and calls within reach, while remote start makes cold mornings and hot afternoons comfortable before you get in. Automatic climate control maintains the cabin at your preferred temperature, and lane departure warning with lane keep assist provides an extra layer of safety on long trips and busy highways. This Chevrolet Silverado 1500 features a spacious interior, supportive seating, and a durable bed ready for work or weekend gear. Modern infotainment and connectivity options pair with practical storage and towing features to make this truck as useful on the jobsite as it is for family drives. Well-maintained and competitively priced, this 2020 Chevy Chevrolet Silverado LT offers the best price in the Muskogee area — exceptional value for a V8-powered 4WD pickup with these safety and convenience features. Schedule a test drive in Muskogee, OK today to experience the performance, comfort, and capability of this Chevrolet Silverado for yourself. Financing options available to help you drive home with confidence.

Equipment
This vehicle is a certified CARFAX 1-owner. This unit features steering wheel audio controls. The rear parking assist technology on it will put you at ease when reversing. The system alerts you as you get closer to an obstruction. This 2020 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 offers Apple CarPlay for seamless connectivity. Lane Keep Assist in this model helps maintain safe driving by gently steering to stay within the lane. This model offers Automatic Climate Control for personalized comfort. Start this 2020 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 from inside with remote start. Keep your hands warm all winter with a heated steering wheel in this 1/2 ton pickup . This 2020 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 has automated speed control that adjusts to maintain a safe following distance, enhancing highway driving convenience. This 2021 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 High Country 4WD Crew Cab in Gray with Jet Black interior, showing 71,000 miles, is available now at Herrin-Gear INFINITI in Jackson, MS. Mississippi truck shoppers searching for used trucks for sale in Jackson MS, full-size luxury pickups Mississippi, and capable trucks across the Southeast consistently choose the Chevrolet Silverado 1500 for its proven power, refined comfort, and all-purpose capability built for Central Mississippi driving.

EXTERIOR AND INTERIOR
The Gray exterior delivers a clean, upscale truck appearance that fits professional use in Jackson and rugged travel throughout Madison, Ridgeland, and beyond. The High Country trim adds premium chrome accents, distinctive badging, and a confident stance that separates it from standard pickups. Inside, the Jet Black leather interior offers a quiet, refined cabin with premium materials, heated and ventilated seating, and generous Crew Cab space designed for both workdays and long highway drives.

COMFORT/TECHNOLOGY/FEATURES
The Silverado High Country blends luxury with utility. Enjoy leather-appointed seating, advanced trailering technology, touchscreen infotainment with smartphone integration, Bose premium audio, head-up display, surround-view camera system, adaptive cruise control, lane-keep assist, blind-spot monitoring, and power-adjustable pedals. The cabin is designed to stay cool quickly in Mississippi heat while remaining comfortable on extended road trips.

ENGINE/PERFORMANCE
Power comes from a strong V8 engine paired with a smooth automatic transmission and 4WD drivetrain. This setup delivers confident acceleration, excellent towing capability, and stable performance on highways, job sites, and uneven terrain. Fuel economy is competitive for a full-size luxury pickup while offering the muscle Mississippi truck buyers expect.

COMPETITOR COMPARISON
Compared with Ford F-150 Platinum, RAM 1500 Limited, GMC Sierra Denali, Toyota Tundra, and Nissan Titan Platinum Reserve, the Silverado High Country stands out for its balance of V8 power, ride comfort, advanced trailering tech, and upscale interior execution. Mississippi buyers appreciate its durability and everyday drivability.

STANDING FAQ BLOCK
Do you offer delivery outside Jackson? Yes.
Can I finance this vehicle? Yes.
Do you accept trade-ins? Yes.
Can I complete the purchase remotely? Yes.
What makes this truck ideal for Mississippi drivers? V8 power, 4WD capability, premium interior comfort, and confident towing performance.

FINANCING/TRADE-IN/SHIPPING
Herrin-Gear INFINITI offers financing for all credit profiles with fast online applications. We provide competitive trade-in values across Mississippi. Nationwide delivery and seamless remote paperwork options are available throughout the Southeast.

MISSISSIPPI LIFESTYLE SUITABILITY
This Silverado High Country 4WD fits Mississippi life perfectly. Ideal for commuting in Jackson, job site use in Brandon and Pearl, professional travel through Madison and Ridgeland, towing needs across Central Mississippi, and road trips to Clinton, Oxford, Starkville, Tupelo, Meridian, Hattiesburg, Gulfport, Biloxi, Memphis, Birmingham, and New Orleans.

FINAL CTA
This 2021 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 High Country 4WD Crew Cab in Gray with Jet Black interior, 71,000 miles, is available now at Herrin-Gear INFINITI in Jackson MS. Serving Jackson, Madison, Ridgeland, Flowood, Brandon, Pearl, Clinton, Oxford, Starkville, Tupelo, Meridian, Hattiesburg, Gulfport, Biloxi, Memphis, Birmingham, and New Orleans. Call or visit today.

Discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and style in this 2021 Ram 1500 Big Horn/Lone Star. With its impressive HEMI 5.7L V8 engine, 4-wheel drive, and a host of premium features, this truck is ready to take on any adventure.

• CARFAX Certified, One Owner

This Big Horn/Lone Star model is equipped with a range of features that elevate your driving experience. The Uconnect 4 infotainment system with an 8.4-inch display keeps you connected and entertained, while the SiriusXM Satellite Radio provides endless entertainment options. The power-folding mirrors and auto-dimming exterior driver mirror add a touch of convenience, and the rear power sliding window allows for easy access to the truck bed.

The exterior of this Ram 1500 exudes a bold, confident presence with its body-color front and rear bumpers, complemented by the striking 20-inch aluminum chrome-clad wheels. The Hydro Blue Pearlcoat paint finish adds a unique and eye-catching touch to this well-equipped truck.

Step inside the cabin, and you'll be greeted by the comfortable and stylish Deluxe Cloth Bucket Seats. The power 8-way driver's seat and power 4-way lumbar support ensure a personalized driving position for maximum comfort on the road. The universal garage door opener and rear 60/40 folding seat further enhance the versatility of this impressive vehicle.

Backed by a CARFAX Certified history and a single previous owner, this 2021 Ram 1500 Big Horn/Lone Star is a testament to quality and reliability. With its exceptional performance, advanced features, and striking appearance, this truck is the perfect choice for those seeking a capable and refined full-size pickup.

Experience the power and sophistication of this 2021 Ram 1500 Big Horn/Lone Star. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can transform your driving experience.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2022 Ram 1500 Laramie. Boasting a powerful HEMI 5.7L V8 engine, this truck delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, with an impressive 15 city and 22 highway MPG.

• 5.7L V8 (HEMI) (eTorque) with Multi Displacement System and Variable Valve Timing
• Sport Appearance Package with premium painted wheels, body-color accents, and performance hood
• Laramie Level I Equipment Group with advanced safety and convenience features

This Laramie trim level sets the standard for premium full-size pickup trucks. The sleek Silver exterior, complemented by the body-color accents, creates a bold and sophisticated look. Step inside the cabin and you'll be greeted by the luxurious Black leather-trimmed bucket seats, offering exceptional comfort and support.

The Laramie Level I Equipment Group takes this truck to the next level, with features like Remote Tailgate Release, Auto High Beam Headlamp Control, Blind Spot & Cross Path Detection, and ParkSense Front/Rear Park Assist. The Sport Appearance Package adds a touch of sportiness with the unique hood, body-color accents, and premium painted wheels.

Versatility is key with the 2022 Ram 1500 Laramie. The rear 60/40 folding seat provides ample cargo space when needed, while the Rear Underseat Compartment Storage offers additional hidden storage solutions. The Trailer Brake Control ensures confident towing capabilities, making this truck a true workhorse.

Elevate your driving experience with the advanced technology features, including the 8.4" Uconnect 5 touchscreen display, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and a 4G LTE Wi-Fi Hotspot. Stay connected and entertained on every journey.

This 2022 Ram 1500 Laramie is a true standout in the full-size pickup segment. With its exceptional performance, premium features, and striking appearance, it's the perfect choice for those who demand the best. Experience the difference for yourself – schedule a test drive today and discover the power and capability of this remarkable truck.

description: Experience the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology with this stunning 2016 Mazda6 i Grand Touring sedan. Finished in elegant Snowflake White Pearl Mica with a plush Parchment interior, this used vehicle exudes sophistication and comfort. Powered by a responsive 2.5-liter four-cylinder engine producing 184 horsepower and 185 lb-ft of torque, it delivers a smooth, fuel-efficient ride with an impressive 26 mpg city and 38 mpg highway. The 6-speed automatic transmission and front-wheel-drive setup make for effortless handling and driving enjoyment, whether you're navigating city streets or open highways. With only 168,603 miles, this Mazda6 offers reliability and value, complemented by advanced features like a backup camera, blind spot monitor, Bluetooth connectivity, collision warning, and cross traffic alert, ensuring safety and convenience at every turn. The luxurious interior boasts heated leather seats, memory seat settings, keyless entry, a sunroof, and a premium audio system, making every drive a pleasure. The Mazda6 i Grand Touring is equipped with a comprehensive suite of technology and comfort features designed to enhance your driving experience. An intuitive 7-inch touch screen infotainment system provides seamless access to navigation, satellite radio, and internet radio apps such as Pandora, Stitcher, and AHA, keeping you entertained and connected on the go. The premium audio system with 11 speakers delivers rich sound quality, while voice-operated Bluetooth, radio, and electronic messaging assistance offer hands-free convenience. Additional features like push start, satellite radio readiness, and a sunroof further elevate this sedan’s appeal, making it a perfect choice for drivers seeking luxury, safety, and advanced technology in a stylish package. 2016 Mazda Mazda6 Safety and Security Features This Mazda6 prioritizes safety with its four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS), providing confident stopping power in various driving conditions. Anti-lockout power door locks prevent accidental lock-ins, while auto-locking door locks enhance security once the vehicle is in motion. An electronic parking brake adds convenience and stability, ensuring your vehicle remains secure when parked. These features work together to deliver peace of mind, making the Mazda6 a reliable and safe choice for daily commuting and long-distance journeys. 2016 Mazda Mazda6 Entertainment and Technology Features Entertainment and connectivity are at the forefront in this Mazda6, featuring a 7-inch touch screen display that consolidates control over various functions. The vehicle’s sound system includes 11 speakers, delivering immersive audio quality whether you're enjoying your favorite music or radio station. Hands-free phone call integration, voice-operated radio, and electronic messaging assistance allow for safe, distraction-free communication while on the road. Satellite radio compatibility and internet radio apps such as Pandora, Stitcher, and AHA keep your entertainment options virtually limitless, making every drive enjoyable and connected. 26/38 description:
Introducing the sleek and stylish 2016 Chevrolet Cruze LS Auto, the perfect combination of performance, efficiency, and modern design. Equipped with a powerful 1.4L Turbo I4 engine, this sedan boasts an impressive 153 horsepower and 177 ft. lbs. of torque, allowing for a smooth and exhilarating driving experience. And with its 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission, you'll have the flexibility to choose between a smooth ride or a more dynamic one.

Step inside the spacious and comfortable cabin of the Cruze LS Auto and you'll be greeted with premium materials and advanced technology. The 6-way adjustable driver's seat ensures maximum comfort, while the 7-inch touchscreen display allows for easy access to your favorite music, contacts, and navigation. Plus, with ample legroom and trunk space, this car is perfect for both daily commutes and road trips.

But the 2016 Chevrolet Cruze LS Auto isn't just about performance and style, it's also incredibly fuel-efficient. With an EPA estimated 30 MPG in the city and 42 MPG on the highway, you'll be able to save on gas without sacrificing power.

Don't miss your chance to own this top-of-the-line sedan. Visit our dealership today to test drive the 2016 Chevrolet Cruze LS Auto and experience the ultimate driving experience.

WHY BUY FROM US
Buy with confidence at Group 1 where every used vehicle, up to 175,000 miles, comes with a one month 1,000-mile limited warranty along with a 3-day 250-mile return policy. NO HAGGLE, NO HASSLE PRICING

MARKET-BASED PRICING

VEHICLE SERVICE CONTRACTS

Introducing the ultimate driving machine - the 2018 BMW 3 Series 320i! This luxurious sedan is equipped with a powerful 2.0L Turbo I4 engine that delivers an impressive 180 horsepower and 200 ft. lbs. of torque. But the excitement doesn't stop there - the 320i also offers superior handling and a smooth ride, making every journey a pleasure. With its impeccable engineering and cutting-edge technology, the 2018 BMW 3 Series 320i is the epitome of luxury and performance.

Discover your next ride at HoneyCar Winchester✨
From scenic drives through Shenandoah to Northern Virginia job sites, this 2020 Honda Ridgeline RTL-E AWD delivers all the comfort, tech, and capability you could ask for. With leather seating, navigation, a power moonroof, and Honda’s legendary all-wheel drive, this used truck is built for every kind of adventure. Available now at our Winchester, VA store!

🛡️ Safety & Driver Assist

🛡️ Blind Spot Information System — Alerts you to vehicles in your blind zone.
🛡️ Collision Mitigation Braking System — Smart protection when it matters.
🛡️ Lane Departure Warning — Helps keep you safely on course.
🛡️ Rearview Camera — Makes reversing and parking easier.
🛡️ Adaptive Cruise Control — Smooth highway drives made safer.

📱 Tech & Audio

📱 Honda Navigation System — Built-in maps with voice guidance.
📱 Apple CarPlay & Android Auto — Sync your smartphone with ease.
📱 SiriusXM Radio — Nonstop music, news, and entertainment.
📱 8-Speaker Premium Audio — Hear your playlists loud and clear.
📱 Truck-Bed Audio System — Turn your Ridgeline into a tailgate party.

♨️ Comfort & Convenience

♨️ Heated Leather Seats — Warmth and luxury for front passengers.
♨️ Heated Steering Wheel — Cozy comfort on cold Winchester mornings.
♨️ Power Moonroof — Let the sun and breeze in on Shenandoah drives.
♨️ Dual-Zone Climate Control — Personalized comfort for driver and passenger.
♨️ Memory Seats — One-touch recall for your perfect position.

⚙️ Performance & Capability

🔑 3.5L V6 Engine — Strong power for commuting or hauling.
🔑 AWD System — All-weather traction for Virginia’s varied roads.
🔑 9-Speed Automatic — Smooth, responsive shifting.
🔑 18" Gray Alloy Wheels — Rugged style meets performance.
🔑 Rear Step Bumper & Bed Audio — Tailgate in style with built-in sound.

🐝 HoneyCar Certified Benefits

✅ 90-day/3,000-mile limited warranty.
✅ Roadside assistance included.
✅ Ally financing options available.
✅ Coverage up to 149,999 miles.
✅ HoneyCare Upgrade available — tire/wheel, paint, key, more.

Available now at our Winchester, VA store.
Whether you're hauling gear through Roanoke or cruising to Charlottesville with the family, this used Honda Ridgeline for sale gives you the versatility of a truck with the comfort of an SUV — all backed by the HoneyCar difference.

At HoneyCar, we make buying used vehicles easy, fun, and stress-free. With a people-first approach, honest pricing, and a team that treats you like family, you’ll find out why we’re Winchester’s go-to for used trucks and more.

This is the car for those who've worked hard and deserve to enjoy the ride. For those who understand that true luxury is about how you feel, not just what you drive.
Fresh Arrival - Your opportunity to elevate every drive starts today.
Life's too short for stressful drives. Choose happiness. Choose Lexus.

Why BUY from BMW of Lafayette? When you choose this Dravit Grey Metallic 2026 BMW XM Label with 306 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! One Owner! What this vehicle includes: Convenience
  • Unresponsive driver assistant - a reaction to inaction. Maybe you fell asleep. Maybe you lost consciousness. No matter how it happens, Unresponsive driver assistant works to help lessen the danger when it does. It detects prolonged driver unresponsiveness, automatically bringing the vehicle to a stop and turning on the hazard lights. If equipped, emergency services will also be contacted. Unresponsive driver assistant is safety that never sleeps.
Safety and Security
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay and Android Auto Compatibility smart device wireless mirroring
Come on in to BMW of Lafayette today at 178 Sagamore Parkway South Lafayette IN 47905 or call to schedule a test drive!

description: Experience the Future of Driving with the 2025 Toyota Sequoia: Hybrid Power, Advanced Safety, and Unmatched Comfort for the Adventurous Family Step into the 2025 Toyota Sequoia, a used vehicle that combines the power of a V6 Hybrid engine with the sophistication of Celestial Silver Metallic. Designed for those who crave adventure without compromising on comfort, this 4D Sport Utility vehicle offers a seamless blend of performance and innovation. The Sequoia s hybrid powertrain, featuring a Turbocharged V6 engine and a Nickel Metal Hydride Traction Battery, ensures both efficiency and power, perfect for long road trips or daily commutes. Safety is paramount with features like Blind Spot Monitor, Lane Keeping Assist, and Rear Collision Mitigation, providing peace of mind for you and your loved ones. The Aerial View Display System and Back-Up Camera make maneuvering in tight spaces a breeze. Enjoy the luxury of heated front seats, a leather steering wheel, and a sun/moonroof, enhancing your driving experience. With a spacious interior that includes a 3rd Row Seat and power-adjustable seating, the Sequoia is ready for any journey. Whether you re towing with its robust Tow Hitch or navigating diverse terrains with Four Wheel Drive, the 2025 Toyota Sequoia is your ultimate companion for exploration and comfort.

description:
Why BUY from BMW of Lafayette? When you choose this Storm Bay Metallic 2025 BMW iX xDrive50 with 4,198 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! What this vehicle includes: Convenience Package ($2,200 value)
  • Iconic Sounds Electric
  • Parking Assistant Plus
  • Harman Kardon Surround Sound System
  • Live Cockpit Pro
  • Surround View with 3D View
Driving Assistance Professional Package ($2,700 value)
  • Active Driving Assistant Pro
  • Highway Assistant
  • Parking Assistant Professional
  • Active Cruise Control with Stop and Go
  • Active Lane Keeping Assistant
  • Traffic Jam Assistant
Sport Package ($2,500 value)
  • 21\' X 9\' Aero Bicolor (style 1012) Wheels
  • Sport Package
  • Specific Additional Contents in Sport Package
Convenience
  • Remote parking - Fit in anywhere! Remote parking system allows you to pull into or out of a space without having to be in the vehicle, simply use the remote control! It's perfect when the cars next to you are too close for you to be able open your doors. With remote parking, any spot is an open spot!
  • GPS linked cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until GPS linked cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed and the system uses GPS navigation data to maintain that speed without driver intervention - including slowing down for curves and anticipating hills. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, GPS linked cruise control.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay and Android Auto Compatibility smart device wireless mirroring
Come on in to BMW of Lafayette today at 178 Sagamore Parkway South Lafayette IN 47905 or call to schedule a test drive!

To determine the recall status of a vehicle, visit https://www.nhtsa.gov/recalls.Discover the ultimate in power, style, and advanced technology with the 2025 Chevrolet Tahoe RST. This exceptional full-size SUV is the perfect blend of rugged capability and refined sophistication, designed to elevate your driving experience.Boasting an impressive array of premium features, the 2025 Tahoe RST is a true standout in its class. Enjoy the exceptional sound quality of the **BOSE AUDIO SYSTEM**, the added convenience of **ADVANCED SAFETY TECHNOLOGY**, and the peace of mind provided by the **BACK UP CAMERA** and **REARVIEW CAMERA**. Indulge in the unparalleled comfort of the **LEATHER SEATS** and the versatility of the **3RD-ROW SEATS**. Stay connected with the **NAVIGATION SYSTEM**, **APPLE CARPLAY**, **ANDROID AUTO**, **BLUETOOTH, HANDS-FREE**, and **SATELLITE RADIO**.This Tahoe RST also comes equipped with the **COMFORT PACKAGE**, which includes a host of additional luxuries such as **MEMORY SETTINGS**, **HEATED STEERING WHEEL**, **HEATED SECOND ROW SEATS**, and **POWER RELEASE SECOND ROW SEATS**. The **PREMIUM WHEELS** and **PREMIUM SOUND SYSTEM** further elevate the driving experience, while the **ALARM SYSTEM** and **TOW PACKAGE** provide added peace of mind and versatility.Powered by the impressive **ECOTEC3 5.3L V8** engine and paired with the **10-SPEED AUTOMATIC TRANSMISSION**, the 2025 Tahoe RST delivers a commanding performance with an impressive **15 MPG** in the city and **20 MPG** on the highway. The **REAR-WHEEL DRIVE** configuration ensures a smooth and responsive ride, while the **PREMIUM SMOOTH RIDE SUSPENSION** provides a refined and comfortable driving experience.Beyond its impressive capabilities, the 2025 Tahoe RST also boasts a striking **BLACK** exterior that exudes a bold and confident presence on the road. The **LED HEADLAMPS**, **LED DAYTIME RUNNING LAMPS**, and **LED TAIL LAMPS** further enhance the vehicle's sleek and modern aesthetic.Whether you're embarking on family adventures, towing heavy loads, or simply seeking a luxurious and capable daily driver, the 2025 Chevrolet Tahoe RST is the perfect choice. Experience the ultimate in power, technology, and style schedule a test drive today and discover the true essence of this exceptional SUV.

2024 Ford Bronco Raptor - Now Available at Mercedes-Benz of Lafayette Drive with Confidence. Backed by Legacy. Discover the perfect blend of performance, utility, style, and value with this 2024 Ford Bronco Raptor, available now at Mercedes-Benz of Lafayette - part of the Moss Motors family, proudly serving Acadiana for over 50 years. Whether you're commuting through Lafayette or cruising down I-10, this Bronco delivers the comfort and capability you expect from a quality pre-owned vehicle. Take a look at what it has to offer... No Accidents! One Owner! Key Features & Packages: Equipment Group 374A High/lux Package
  • 10-Speed Automatic Transmission
  • Engine: 3.0L EcoBoost V6
  • 4.7 Axle Ratio
  • 6,100 lbs GVWR
  • B&O Sound System by Bang and Olufsen
  • 37 X 12.5R17 All-Terrain Tires
  • 17\' Black High Gloss-Painted Aluminum Wheels
Interior Carbon Fiber Pack 6 ($1,725 value)
    Blue with Black Onyx Leather-Trimmed/Vinyl Seats ($2,995 value)
    • Includes Blue with Black Onyx leather-trimmed/vinyl seats, 10-way power adjustable driver's seat, 8-way power adjustable passenger's seat, and second row armrest with two beverage holders.
    Safety and Security
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Apple CarPlay and Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
    • SYNC 4 AppLink/Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
    • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
    Other Notable Features/Options ENGINE: 3.0L ECOBOOST V6 One Owner! Every used vehicle at Mercedes-Benz of Lafayette undergoes a thorough multi-point inspection by certified technicians. Whether it's a Mercedes-Benz or another quality make, we stand behind each vehicle we sell because our name has meant trust in Lafayette since 1979. description: Discover this stunning 2016 Ram 1500 Longhorn Limited, a used pickup truck that combines rugged capability with luxurious comfort. Finished in Bright White Clearcoat with a sophisticated black interior, this vehicle boasts a powerful 5.7-liter V8 engine delivering 395 horsepower and 410 lb-ft of torque, ensuring it’s ready for anything from towing to daily driving. With only 163,502 miles on the odometer, this truck has been meticulously maintained and offers a premium driving experience. It features an 8-speed automatic transmission and full-time 4WD, providing exceptional handling in all conditions. The Ram 1500 Longhorn Limited is loaded with high-end features, including a navigation system, premium audio with 506 watts and eight speakers, Bluetooth connectivity, satellite radio, and a large 8.4-inch touchscreen infotainment system. Enhancing its style and functionality are 20 x 9-inch polished aluminum forged wheels, a tow package with added tow hooks, an anti-spin rear differential, and a limited appearance package with bright bumpers and chrome side molding. For added convenience, this truck includes a power sunroof, leather heated seats with memory settings, and the RamBox cargo management system, offering versatile storage and bed extension options. Safety and security are prioritized with front and rear parking sensors, ABS, power door locks, and brake drying technology. 2016 Ram 1500 Safety and Security Features This Ram 1500 Longhorn Limited is equipped with front and rear parking sensors, making parking and maneuvering easier and safer. It also features four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) for improved stopping power and control in emergency situations. Power door locks enhance security, while brake drying technology helps maintain braking performance in wet conditions, providing peace of mind during every drive. 2016 Ram 1500 Entertainment and Technology Features The vehicle is packed with advanced entertainment and technology features, including a voice-operated radio and HD radio for crystal-clear audio. Surround sound speakers deliver an immersive listening experience, complemented by an eight-speaker system and a subwoofer for deep bass. The 8.4-inch touchscreen display serves as the central hub for navigation with real-time traffic updates, electronic messaging assistance with a read function, and a touch screen interface that simplifies control of all multimedia functions, making every journey enjoyable and connected. 2016 Ram 1500 Performance Features Performance is at the forefront of this Ram 1500 with its electronic high-low 4WD selector, allowing drivers to switch between two-wheel and four-wheel drive modes for optimal traction. The part-time 4WD system with an on-demand setting provides versatility and confidence whether you're on rough terrain or paved roads. These features ensure this pickup is as capable as it is luxurious, ready to handle every challenge with ease.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2022 Chevrolet Tahoe Z71. Boasting a commanding presence and uncompromising capability, this SUV is the perfect companion for your adventures.

Highlighted features include:
• Luxury Package
• Power Panoramic Sunroof
• Max Trailering Package
• 2nd Row Bucket Seats with Power Release
• Heated Steering Wheel
• HD Surround Vision
• Rear Pedestrian Alert
• Memory Settings
• Electronic Limited-Slip Differential
• Magnetic Ride Control Suspension

Under the hood, the EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine and 10-speed automatic transmission deliver a thrilling blend of power and efficiency, with an impressive 4WD system that gives you the confidence to tackle any terrain. With a fuel economy of 15 city/20 highway MPG, this Tahoe Z71 strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality.

The Luxury Package elevates your driving experience with premium features like heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a power-folding third-row seat. The panoramic sunroof floods the cabin with natural light, creating an airy and open atmosphere. For your towing needs, the Max Trailering Package, complete with an extra capacity cooling system, ensures your Tahoe is ready to handle your biggest adventures.

Cutting-edge technology abounds, with the Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Premium System, Bose 9-speaker audio, and a suite of advanced safety features, including Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Rear Pedestrian Alert. The HD Surround Vision camera provides a 360-degree view, making maneuvering a breeze.

Meticulously maintained and well-equipped, this 2022 Chevrolet Tahoe Z71 is a true standout in its class. Experience the perfect blend of power, capability, and refined luxury. Schedule a test drive today and discover how this exceptional SUV can elevate your driving experience.

description: Just arrived is this gratuitously loaded, ONE-OWNER, NONSMOKER, TWIN-TURBOCHARGED 2022 Lincoln Navigator 4x4! This cutting-edge monster of an SUV boasts lots of cargo room, an easy-to-use technology interface, strong turbocharged V6 with ample power for towing, AND plenty of advanced driver aids! Key Accolades & Positive Mentions: Top-Ranked Luxury SUV: Consistently placed at the top of full-size luxury SUV rankings by U.S. News and MotorTrend, often beating German competitors. Best in Class: Described as the ''best vehicle Lincoln builds right now'' and the ''big boss'' in the luxury SUV segment by MotorTrend. Owner Satisfaction: Ranked highly in J.D. Power studies for overall appeal and satisfaction. Its ten-speed transmission delivers improved overall performance, with enhanced acceleration at the low and mid ranges of the power band. Features include optimized wide-span gear spacing coupled with drag-reduction actions plus three overdrive gears. While towing, decreased ratio distance ensures smoother shifts. With its odometer now hovering around the 42,133 mark, it is STILL COVERED under the balance of the factory BUMPER-TO-BUMPER warranty until August 2026 or 50,000 miles (whichever occurs first)! Additionally, the engine, transmission and drive axles are STILL COVERED under the balance of the factory powertrain warranty until 2028 or 70,000 miles! Standard driver-assistance features: Forward collision warning Pedestrian detection Forward automatic emergency braking Lane-keep assist Evasive-steering assist (helps steer the vehicle to avoid collisions) Adaptive cruise control Blind-spot monitoring Rear cross-traffic alert Rearview camera Surround-view camera system Front and rear parking sensors Park assist MyKey (allows you to do things      Convenience
    • Cruise control maintains a preset vehicle speed, automatically increasing or decreasing throttle to maintain that speed.
    Safety and Security
    • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
    • Brake assist senses panic braking from the speed of the brake pedal's travel and applies all available power brake boost.
    • The vehicle is equipped with sensors that monitor the driver. If the sensors determine the driver is drowsy or inattentive, the vehicle will flash or sound a warning.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.

Its distinguished King Ranch trim showcases distinctive styling, complemented by the King Ranch Chrome Appearance Package that adds a touch of elegance and sophistication.Inside, the Java leather interior exudes a sense of warmth and luxury, enhanced by the detailed craftsmanship and attention to detail that the King Ranch is known for. description: Treat yourself to the ultimate driving experience in this stunning Lunar Blue Metallic 2022 Mercedes-Benz GLE 350 SUV. This vehicle is a standout choice, coming with a clean CARFAX, no damage history, and the peace of mind that only a Factory Certified car can offer. Its been kept in top-tier condition and includes all books, keys, and service records. With its sophisticated color and 21-inch twin 5-spoke wheels, this vehicle perfectly balances a rugged spirit with pure elegance.The interior of this Mercedes-Benz GLE 350 SUV is designed to be your personal sanctuary. You'll find genuine wood inserts across the dashboard, console, and door panels that create a high-end feel. Comfort is a top priority with heated and ventilated front seats, ensuring you stay cozy in the winter and cool during the summer. The massive 12.3-inch touchscreen display runs the advanced MBUX system, giving you easy access to navigation and your favorite apps through Apple CarPlay or Android Auto.If you love sunshine and great music, this Mercedes-Benz GLE 350 SUV has you covered. It features a gorgeous Panorama power tilt and sliding sunroof that opens up the cabin to the world around you. For the audiophiles, the Burmester Surround Sound System delivers crystal-clear audio that turns every drive into a concert. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend getaway, the premium atmosphere inside this vehicle makes every mile feel special.This Mercedes-Benz GLE 350 SUV is also built for utility and ease of use. It comes equipped with a trailer hitch and increased towing capacity, making it ready for your outdoor adventures. The Surround View System and Parking Assist make navigating into tight spots effortless by giving you a clear view of everything around you. Plus, features like the power liftgate and illuminated running boards add a layer of convenience that makes loading up the family or gear simpler than ever.Safety and smart technology are at the heart of this modern machine. With auto high-beam headlights, rain-sensing wipers, and an emergency communication system, this Mercedes-Benz GLE 350 SUV is constantly working to keep you safe. The power front seats include driver memory settings that link to the auto tilt-away steering wheel, so the car always feels like it was custom-made just for you. Its a versatile and powerful vehicle that truly does it all.727-306-9453 Our Mercedes-Benz Factory Certification program is a curation of the very best Pre-Owned Mercedes-Benz vehicles available. Each and every one has passed a rigorous, 162-point Factory inspection and been completely reconditioned inside and out. All services and maintenance are up to date, including tires, brakes, belts, hoses and all fluids. Comes with 24/7 Roadside Assistance, Trip-Interruption Coverage, CARFAX service records available.*Burmester is a registered trademark of Burmester Audiosysteme GmbH, Berlin, Germany.
