description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and capability with this 2017 Hyundai Santa Fe Sport 2.4 Base. This versatile SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience and take you on unforgettable adventures.

Boasting a sleek silver exterior, this Santa Fe Sport is more than just a pretty face. It's equipped with a robust 2.4L I4 DGI DOHC 16V engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 6-Speed Automatic with Shiftronic transmission, delivering an impressive 21 MPG in the city and 27 MPG on the highway.

Key features include:
• Backup Camera
• Voice Recognition
• Bluetooth Hands-Free
• Super Clean
• Low Miles
• Local Trade

Beyond the essentials, this Santa Fe Sport is packed with premium amenities to enhance your daily drive. Enjoy the convenience of the Cargo Tray and All Weather Floor Mats, keeping your vehicle's interior pristine. The Cargo Net provides additional storage solutions, ensuring you have ample space for all your needs.

Under the hood, the 2.4L engine provides the power you need, while the 4-Wheel Disc Brakes and Electronic Stability Control deliver confidence-inspiring handling. The Four Wheel Independent Suspension and Speed-Sensing Steering further enhance the driving dynamics, making every journey a pleasure.

Step inside the spacious cabin and discover the thoughtful design that puts your comfort first. The Stain-Resistant Cloth Seating Surfaces and Multi-Adjustable Bucket Seats provide exceptional support, while the Tilt and Telescoping Steering Wheel allows you to find your perfect driving position.

Connectivity is key, and this Santa Fe Sport delivers with features like the AM/FM/SiriusXM/CD/MP3 Audio System, Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls, and Bluetooth Hands-Free technology. Stay entertained and connected on the go.

Safety is paramount, and this Hyundai is equipped with a suite of advanced features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Knee Airbag, and Occupant Sensing Airbag. The Rear Camera and Low Tire Pressure Warning further enhance your peace of mind.

Experience the perfect blend of style, comfort, and capability with this 2017 Hyundai Santa Fe Sport 2.4 Base. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional SUV can elevate your driving experience.

Enjoy the convenience of remote keyless entry, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and an advanced infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The spacious cabin provides ample room for passengers and cargo, with a split-folding rear seat for added versatility. Safety is also a top priority, with features like ABS brakes, electronic stability control, and an emergency communication system to give you peace of mind on the road.

Boasting a sleek silver exterior and stylish alloy wheels, this Tacoma SR5 V6 not only looks great but is built to last. With its rugged construction and Toyota's reputation for reliability, you can count on this truck to serve you well for years to come.

The driver will appreciate the heated steering wheel, memory settings, and advanced infotainment system, keeping you connected and in control.

Under the hood, the Traverse High Country is powered by a robust 3.6L V6 SIDI VVT engine, delivering an impressive 310 horsepower and 266 lb-ft of torque. Safety is paramount in the Traverse High Country, with a host of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Keep Assist, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, ensuring you and your loved ones arrive at your destination with confidence.

Experience the epitome of luxury and capability in the 2021 Chevrolet Traverse High Country. This exceptional SUV is the perfect blend of power, technology, and refined style, making it the ultimate choice for the discerning driver. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Traverse High Country should be your next vehicle.

description: Introducing the all-new 2021 Mazda CX-5 Grand Touring SUV, a powerful and stylish ride that will take your driving experience to the next level. This SUV is equipped with a 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission for smooth and effortless shifting. And with its efficient gasoline engine, you can enjoy a fuel-efficient drive without compromising on performance. The exterior of the CX-5 Grand Touring is designed to turn heads with its sleek and modern design. From its bold front grille to its stylish LED headlights, this SUV exudes confidence and sophistication. The spacious interior offers luxurious amenities such as leather-trimmed seats, a power moonroof, and advanced technology features for your comfort and convenience. Under the hood, the 2021 CX-5 Grand Touring boasts a powerful 2.5-liter 4-cylinder engine that delivers an impressive 187 horsepower and 186 lb-ft of torque. With Mazda's SKYACTIV technology, this SUV provides a smooth and responsive ride, whether you're cruising on the highway or navigating busy city streets. But the CX-5 Grand Touring isn't just about power and style, it also prioritizes safety. With advanced safety features such as blind-spot monitoring, lane-keep assist, and automatic emergency braking, you can have peace of mind knowing that you and your passengers are protected on every journey. Don't miss your chance to own the 2021 Mazda CX-5 Grand Touring SUV. Come see it for yourself and take it for a test drive at our dealership. Experience the thrill and luxury of this SUV and make it yours today. Hurry, this SUV won't stay on our lot for long!

description:
In developing our founding commitment ( The Cardinale Way ), we selected key words that are as meaningful to you as they are to our mission. One of those is “relationship.” With every introduction, we are looking, not for a single transaction, but to “develop” a relationship with our customers...not just a good relationship, but an “outstanding” relationship that will outlast your car. Another key element is that “everybody wins”. In a time when most people believe winners create losers, we endeavor to satisfy everybody involved. It means knowing our product well and our customer even better. It means listening and caring and understanding that people buy their second-most expensive item from people they trust. Whether you are a car enthusiast, or you just need a reliable ride, the right car for you means buying exactly what you need and ideally what you want. Over forty years ago, we entered the automobile business driven by a passion for people, and recognizing cars as a “vehicle” for creating meaningful connections. We also understood that helping people select, purchase and finance one of the most important tools of your daily life is a valuable pursuit. Our priority is and has always been making sure your new or used-car buying experience is both satisfying and successful. Within the Cardinale Automotive Group, we know that satisfying a wide range of needs requires a diversity of quality cars. We offer new Audi, BMW, GMC, Harley Davidson, Hyundai, Mazda, Nissan, Toyota and Volkswagen cars, along with used cars, trucks and SUVs by top manufacturers. We are committed to helping you find the right car, assisting you in choosing the right financing options, and becoming your trusted automobile dealer. Our relationship begins with our introduction and continues through the purchase, the financing, the service of the car and beyond. We look forward to developing an outstanding relationship with you.

description:
The 2021 Ram 1500 Big Horn/Lone Star offers a commanding blend of modern capability and exceptional value, finished in a clean Bright White Clearcoat exterior. Powered by the legendary 5.7L HEMI V8 engine with eTorque mild hybrid technology delivering 395 horsepower and 410 lb-ft of torque, this full-size truck provides robust towing power and smooth performance through its efficient 8-speed automatic transmission and an advanced electronic shift-on-the-fly four-wheel-drive system for confident traction in all conditions.

The popular Big Horn/Lone Star trim outfits the Ram 1500 with distinctive 18-inch aluminum wheels, all-season tires, and a chrome grille. Inside, you'll find premium cloth and vinyl-trimmed seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel with audio controls, and a functional yet modern interior. The spacious Crew Cab offers best-in-class rear legroom and versatile storage solutions, along with dual-zone automatic climate control and an 8.4-inch touchscreen Uconnect 4C NAV system for work and weekend versatility.

Advanced technology features include the Uconnect infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, an available 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot, and a digital rearview mirror. The Ram 1500 also boasts an available Class IV receiver hitch.

Engineered for both hard work and smart value, this Ram 1500 achieves an EPA-estimated 15 MPG city/21 MPG highway while offering a formidable 11,610 pounds of maximum towing capacity when properly equipped.

Experience Hassle-Free Shopping at Story Ford:

- Premium Quality Assurance: Rest assured with our meticulous vehicle inspections and reconditioning, averaging over $2,000 per car, ensuring your peace of mind when purchasing a pre-owned vehicle. That's why they're all backed by our 7-Day Like it or Return it Money Back Guarantee.

- Non-commissioned Sales Consultants: Means no pushy sales tactics, just friendly professionals to help you find the best car for your needs.

- Unmatched Transparency: Prior to your purchase, gain full visibility into the service history of the vehicle, ensuring complete transparency and confidence in your decision.

- Our Best Price Upfront: We recognize the extensive research done by shoppers, hence we offer highly competitive prices online to match your needs and expectations.

- Express Checkout for Time Efficiency: Streamline your purchase process by completing most of the deal remotely, whether from the comfort of your workplace or home, saving you valuable time.

description: Buckle up and get ready to hit the road in this sleek and powerful 2017 Black Chevrolet Silverado 1500! With its rear axle ratio and pickup box, this truck is ready to handle any task with ease. The GVWR ensures that you can load up without worry, while the rear-wheel drive provides a smooth and responsive driving experience.Under the hood, the heavy-duty battery and powerful alternator keep this Silverado running smoothly, while the fully-boxed frame guarantees durability in any situation. Whether you're cruising down the highway or tackling tough terrain, the Electric Power Steering and four-wheel disc brakes with DURALIFE rotors provide precise control and stopping power.This Silverado doesn't just deliver strong performance - it also boasts a rugged and stylish design. The Black bumpers, corner step rear bumper, and chrome grille surround give this truck a bold and commanding presence on the road. The cab-mounted cargo area lamps and solar-absorbing tinted glass add practicality and convenience to the mix.Hop inside and you'll find a comfortable and functional interior. The rear full-width folding bench seat ensures plenty of space for passengers or cargo, while the Graphite-colored rubberized-vinyl floor covering is durable and easy to clean. The Tilt-Wheel steering column, power windows, and cruise control make driving a breeze, while the single-zone air conditioning keeps you cool and comfortable.Safety is a top priority in this Silverado, with features like StabiliTrak stability control, dual-stage frontal airbags, and Teen Driver mode for peace of mind on every journey. Plus, with a Carfax report available, you can hit the road with confidence knowing the history of this reliable truck.Whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing a trailer, or simply enjoying a weekend adventure, this Black 2017 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 is the perfect companion for all your driving needs. 2024 Toyota Corolla LE Vehicle DescriptionIntroductionThe 2024 Toyota Corolla LE is a sleek and practical compact sedan that blends everyday usability with modern comfort and efficiency. Known for its long-standing reputation for reliability and value, the Corolla LE delivers a smooth and confident driving experience whether you re commuting, running errands, or heading out on a weekend drive. With thoughtful interior features, intuitive connectivity, and a refined design, the Corolla LE offers a well-rounded package that suits a wide range of lifestyles. From its comfortable cabin to its efficient powertrain, this sedan makes every journey enjoyable and dependable.Performance
  • Engine: 2.0-liter 4-cylinder
  • Horsepower: 169 hp
  • Torque: 151 lb-ft
  • Transmission: Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT)
  • Drivetrain: Front-Wheel Drive (FWD)
  • Suspension tuned for balanced ride and handling
  • Fuel economy optimized for city and highway driving
The 2024 Toyota Corolla LE s 2.0-liter engine delivers responsive and efficient performance that s well-suited for daily driving needs. Paired with a smooth-shifting CVT, power is delivered seamlessly to the front wheels, helping balance performance with excellent fuel efficiency. The suspension system offers a comfortable ride with composed handling that enhances confidence on both urban streets and open highways. With its efficient drivetrain and refined tuning, the Corolla LE provides a satisfying and dependable driving experience that s comfortable for everyday use.This combination of smooth power delivery and engaging dynamics creates a driving experience that feels composed, responsive, and enjoyable whether you re headed to work or out on a weekend adventure.Interior & Comfort
  • Seating Capacity: 5 passengers
  • Premium cloth seating surfaces
  • Dual-zone automatic climate control
  • 8-inch touchscreen infotainment display
  • Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration
  • Bluetooth hands-free connectivity and USB ports
  • Spacious seating with ample headroom and legroom
  • Tilt and telescopic steering column with mounted controls
Inside, the 2024 Corolla LE offers a welcoming and thoughtfully designed cabin that prioritizes comfort and connectivity. The seating provides supportive comfort for both short trips and longer drives, while dual-zone automatic climate control helps maintain a pleasant interior atmosphere for all occupants. The intuitive infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto keeps your favorite apps, media, and navigation easily accessible. With generous interior room and smart storage solutions, the Corolla LE s cabin enhances everyday practicality and comfort.This combination of technology and comfort features makes the interior feel modern, useful, and enjoyable perfect for daily driving and long journeys alike.Dimensions & Capacity
  • Wheelbase: Balanced for stability and passenger space
  • Overall Length: Sleek sedan profile with practical interior room
  • Width: Comfortable seating space front to back
  • Height: Streamlined design with good visibility
  • Passenger Capacity: 5 occupants
  • Trunk Volume: Generous cargo space for luggage and daily essentials
The 2024 Toyota Corolla LE s dimensions offer a roomy and comfortable interior while maintaining a compact and easy-to-maneuver exterior size. Its well-proportioned cabin provides plenty of headroom and legroom for passengers, and the trunk offers generous cargo space for groceries, luggage, or gear. Whether it s packing for a weekend getaway or daily errands, this sedan s interior volume and layout make life easier and more enjoyable.Exterior Features
  • Modern aerodynamic design with clean lines
  • Signature Toyota grille and comfortable profile
  • LED daytime running lights
  • Body-color exterior mirrors and trim
  • Stylish alloy wheels with contemporary finish
  • Sleek, sophisticated design for a confident road presence
The exterior of the 2024 Corolla LE presents a refined and contemporary look that fits a variety of driving environments. Its aerodynamic profile helps improve efficiency while giving the vehicle a modern and confident appearance. LED daytime running lights and stylish alloy wheels add visual appeal, while body-color accents give the Corolla a cohesive, polished look on the road.Safety & Driver Assistance
  • Toyota Safety Sense suite standard
    • Pre-Collision System with Pedestrian Detection
    • Lane Departure Alert with Steering Assist
    • Dynamic Radar Cruise Control
    • Automatic High Beams
  • Star Safety System
  • Rearview camera
  • Anti-lock Braking System (ABS) and Traction Control
  • Tire Pressure Monitoring System
Safety is a cornerstone of the 2024 Corolla LE, with Toyota Safety Sense offering a robust set of standard driver-assist technologies designed to help enhance awareness and protect occupants. From forward collision warning to adaptive cruise control, these systems work together to support confident driving in a variety of conditions. Combined with a strong foundation of core safety features, the Corolla LE helps deliver peace of mind for both drivers and passengers.SummaryThe 2024 Toyota Corolla LE is a dependable and modern compact sedan that delivers a comfortable, connected, and efficient driving experience. Its capable 2.0-liter engine and smooth CVT provide balanced performance for everyday driving, while the well-appointed interior offers comfort, technology, and smart storage for passengers and cargo alike. With a refined exterior design and an extensive suite of standard safety features, this Corolla model inspires confidence and enjoyment in every mile. Whether you re commuting in the city, cruising on the highway, or heading out for a weekend escape, the 2024 Toyota Corolla LE offers a confident, comfortable, and practical ride that fits seamlessly into your lifestyle.

description:
Experience the ultimate in power, technology, and comfort with this exceptional 2024 Ford F-150 Platinum. Boasting a stunning White exterior and a host of premium features, this truck is the epitome of rugged sophistication.

• EQUIPMENT GROUP 702A HIGH: Includes Twin Panel Moonroof, Continuously Controlled Damping, Heads-Up Display, Radio: B&O Unleashed Sound System by Bang & Olufsen, HD Radio and 14 speakers including subwoofer
• 3.5L V6 Hybrid Twin Turbocharged (PowerBoost) (FULL-HYBRID) (Includes Pro Power Onboard 2.4KW and Removes 36 Gallon Fuel Tank, GVWR: 7,350 lbs Payload Package & Electronic Locking with 3.73 Axle Ratio) (*GROSS*)
• WHEELS: 22" GLOSS BLACK W/INSERTS
• Tires: 22"
• TOUGH BED SPRAY-IN BEDLINER
• WHEEL WELL LINER

This F-150 Platinum is more than just a work truck, it's a masterpiece of engineering and design. The 3.5L PowerBoost Full-Hybrid V6 engine delivers exceptional power and efficiency, with an impressive 22 city and 24 highway MPG. The 10-speed automatic transmission and 4WD system ensure seamless performance, whether you're navigating the city streets or tackling rugged terrain.

Step inside and be captivated by the premium cabin. The unique multi-contour leather bucket seats offer unparalleled comfort and support, while the heated and ventilated front seats and heated rear seats keep you cozy in any weather. The SYNC 4 infotainment system with enhanced voice recognition and the 14-speaker B&O sound system provide a truly immersive entertainment experience.

Safety and technology are also at the forefront of this F-150 Platinum. The advanced driver-assistance features, including the Heads-Up Display, Continuously Controlled Damping, and 911 Assist, work together to keep you and your passengers secure. The Tough Bed Spray-In Bedliner and Wheel Well Liner provide added protection and durability for your cargo.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, towing a trailer, or simply enjoying the open road, this 2024 Ford F-150 Platinum is the ultimate companion. With its uncompromising performance, premium amenities, and exceptional safety features, it's the perfect choice for the discerning truck enthusiast.

We invite you to experience the power and sophistication of this remarkable vehicle firsthand. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this F-150 Platinum can transform your driving experience.

description: The 2026 BMW M5 Sedan is a stunning blend of luxury, performance, and cutting-edge technology, designed to offer an exhilarating driving experience. This vehicle is dressed in a sleek Black Sapphire Metallic exterior, exuding an aura of sophistication and power. The interior complements this with a luxurious Black Merino Leather Upholstery, providing a plush and comfortable environment for both driver and passengers. Under the hood, this M5 is powered by a formidable Twin Turbo Gas/Electric V-8 4.4 L/268 engine, paired with an automatic transmission and an all-wheel-drive system. This plug-in hybrid vehicle combines the best of both worlds, offering impressive power and efficiency. The active suspension and M Compound Brakes with red calipers ensure a smooth and controlled ride, while the aluminum wheels and performance tires enhance its sporty appeal. Key features of the 2026 BMW M5 Sedan include: - Driving Assistance Professional Package: - Lane Change Assistant - Partial Automated Driving - Hands-free driving up to 40 mph on selected highways - Traffic Jam Assistant - Executive Package: - Front Ventilated Seats - Parking View with 3D View (Surround View) - Interior Camera - Power Rear Sunshade & Rear Side Window Shades - BMW Iconic Glow Kidney Grille - Parking Assistant Plus - Interior Comfort and Convenience: - Front and Rear Heated Seats - Heated Steering Wheel - Power Driver and Passenger Seats with Adjustable Lumbar Support - Keyless Entry and Start - Multi-Zone Climate Control - Panoramic Sun/Moonroof - Technology and Connectivity: - Premium Sound System with Satellite Radio - Bluetooth Connection - GPS Navigation System - Heads-Up Display - Smart Device Integration - Safety and Driver Assistance: - Blind Spot Monitor - Cross-Traffic Alert - Lane Departure Warning and Lane Keeping Assist - Front and Rear Collision Mitigation - Back-Up Camera and Automatic Parking The exterior design is further enhanced by the BMW Iconic Glow Kidney Grille and a rear spoiler, adding to its dynamic and aggressive stance. The vehicle also features a power liftgate for added convenience. Overall, the 2026 BMW M5 Sedan is a remarkable vehicle that combines luxury, performance, and advanced technology, making it an ideal choice for those who seek both comfort and thrill in their driving experience.

description:
2023 BENTLEY FLYING SPUR S

TOURING SPECIFICATION, PANORAMIC SUNROOF, DIAMOND QUILTING, & MORE!

OVERVIEW
The Bentley Flying Spur is among the best of the best when it comes to luxury sedans––built to pamper passengers and thrill its driver. Finished in classy Beluga paint and hand-built in England, this Flying Spur Speed produces 542 horsepower and 568 lb-ft of torque from its 4.0L twin-turbo V8 engine, paired to an 8-speed automatic transmission and Bentley's advanced all-wheel-drive system. The result is a 0-60 mph time of just 4.0 seconds and a top speed of 177 mph. It rides on an adaptive air suspension that's remarkably supple given its 5,200-pound curb weight, offering passengers a supremely comfortable and composed experience. Visually, the Flying Spur displays its performance intent with subtle aggression. Aerodynamic enhancements, darker accent finishes, and bespoke badging distinguish it from its brethren. A bold Diamond matrix grille, exclusive 22-inch wheels, and an illuminated Flying B radiator mascot project elegance in every detail. Craftsmanship and high-quality materials take priority in the Flying Spur's cabin, with the added benefits of advanced tech for the driver's convenience. Inside standouts are Beluga leather seats with diamond quilting, a panoramic glass sunroof, and leather-covered door panels with a unique 3-D diamond design. Rear passengers enjoy luxury touches such as power-adjustable climate controlled seats as well as a Bang & Olufsen sound system. The 2023 Bentley Flying Spur S is one of the most refined luxury sedans on the market, distinguished not only by its exclusivity but by its balance of unrivaled performance, cutting-edge technology, and handcrafted British luxury.

description:
Experience the epitome of luxury and performance in this captivating 2024 Lexus LS 500 Base. Meticulously crafted with an unwavering commitment to quality, this exceptional vehicle is poised to redefine your driving experience.

Indulge in a comprehensive suite of premium features, including:

• Luxury Package with Adaptive Variable Air Suspension, Four-Zone Climate Concierge, and Heated & Ventilated Rear Seats
• Mark Levinson Audio System with 23 speakers and 2,400-watt reference surround sound
• Panorama Glass Roof for a breathtaking open-air experience
• 20-inch Dark Gray Metallic Split 20-Spoke Alloy Wheels
• Lexus Safety System+ A Package with advanced safety technologies

Step inside this exquisitely appointed cabin and be enveloped in the finest materials, including Semi-Aniline Leather-Trimmed Seats and Premium Wood Trim. Enjoy the unparalleled comfort of the 28-way power-adjustable passenger seat with multifunction massage, as well as the convenience of the 18-way power-reclining outboard rear seats with memory.

Beneath the sleek exterior lies a powerful 6-cylinder DOHC engine mated to a smooth-shifting 10-speed automatic transmission, delivering a remarkable balance of performance and efficiency. With an EPA-estimated 27 highway mpg, this Lexus LS 500 Base offers the perfect blend of power and practicality.

As a Lexus L/Certified pre-owned vehicle, this LS 500 comes with an unparalleled level of confidence and peace of mind. Enjoy the benefits of our comprehensive Lexus Certified Warranty, including an unlimited-mileage warranty up to 6 years, as well as a complimentary Maintenance Plan covering the first four basic factory-scheduled maintenance services for 2 years or 20,000 miles.

Don't miss the opportunity to experience the pinnacle of luxury and craftsmanship. Schedule a test drive today and discover the true essence of the Lexus LS 500 Base.

NO HIDDEN FEES! ALL RECONDITIONING COSTS ARE FULLY INCLUDED IN OUR PRICES.

PREMIUM PACKAGE, M SPORT PACKAGE, PANORAMIC ROOF, NAVIGATION, 14.9" TOUCHSCREEN, 20" WHEELS, HEAD-UP DISPLAY, LEATHER SEATS, BOWER & WILKINS SURROUND SYSTEM, BLIND SPOT MONITOR, GLASS CONTROLS AND TOUCHSCREEN DOOR CONTROLS!!

Indulge in flagship luxury and advanced performance with this Alpine White 2025 BMW 7 Series 740i xDrive AWD, powered by a smooth and responsive 3.0L TwinPower Turbo I6 engine paired with an 8-speed automatic sport transmission and intelligent xDrive all-wheel drive. This premium BMW sedan is equipped with the Premium Package and M Sport Package Pro, offering refined comfort through heated front and rear seats, a heated steering wheel, memory seating, and elegant glass interior controls. Cutting-edge technology takes center stage with a stunning 14.9-inch touchscreen, BMW Maps Navigation, Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, Connected Package Pro, and immersive Bowers & Wilkins surround sound. Advanced safety and driver-assist features include Blind Spot Monitoring, ACC Stop & Go with Active Driving Assistant, Heads-Up Display, Surround View with 3D View, and Parking Assistant Professional. Finished with the iconic illuminated kidney grille and bold 20-inch M Aero bicolor wheels, the 2025 BMW 740i xDrive delivers an exceptional blend of luxury, innovation, and dynamic driving confidence.

- Cars Land is a family owned and operated business that thrives by providing the highest quality of customer service and special cars. You can buy with confidence and note that we apply the highest ethics and standard of doing business by being respectful towards our customers and applying all ADOT & state rules and regulations. Cars Land is ready to do the extra mile to ensure the smoothness of the sale and would be more than happy to virtually show the full aspect of the car for out of state buyers.

- We take all types of credit score. Being connected to all the big banks and credit unions allows us to finance our customers and also provide extended warranties , Gap, Tint & ceramic coating features. Start your credit applications on our website to get you approved and feel free to call us on 480-947-2267 or email us so we can start the process.

- All advertised prices exclude the sales taxes, registration, tint & ceramic, finance charges, any dealer document preparation charge, and any emission testing charge. While we try to make sure that all prices posted here are accurate at all times, we cannot be responsible for typographical and other errors that may appear on the site. For all cars under warranty or for any warranty from the manufacturer, we ask all our clients to check directly with the manufacturer or any franchise dealership to answer any question related to that. We always strive for the highest quality listings and descriptions, however, we are human and do occasionally make mistakes. Please understand not all vehicles come with 2 keys, owner s manuals, floor mats, Navigation software, and any other factory installed equipment. We strive to photograph everything that comes with the car and usually list all accessories that accompany our vehicles. We ask that you confirm all aspects, condition, and accessories that come with our vehicles with your sales consultant. Miles can vary on the car as well due to test drives and service requirements. Contact us if you have any questions or concerns and our friendly staff will assist.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2025 BMW 7 Series 740i xDrive. Boasting a sleek Gray exterior and a meticulously crafted interior, this BMW is the epitome of luxury and performance.

• BMW Unlimited Mile Warranty until June 2030!
• Original MSRP $105,805
• Driving Assistance Professional Package
• M Sport Package Pro
• Premium Package

Powered by a potent 3.0L I6 DOHC 24V TwinPower Turbo engine, this 7 Series delivers an impressive 24 city/31 highway MPG, ensuring both exhilaration and efficiency. The 8-Speed Automatic Sport transmission and xDrive all-wheel-drive system provide seamless power delivery and exceptional handling, making this BMW a true joy to drive.

The Driving Assistance Professional Package equips this 7 Series with cutting-edge technology, including Highway Assistant, Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop & Go, and Active Driving Assistant Pro, providing you with advanced safety and convenience features. The Premium Package further enhances your driving experience with Parking Assistant Professional, a Surround View camera system, and an Illuminated Kidney Grille.

This 7 Series is a BMW Certified pre-owned vehicle, meaning it has undergone a rigorous inspection and comes with the peace of mind of a comprehensive warranty. With only 12,170 miles on the odometer, this BMW is ready to provide you with years of exceptional performance and luxury.

The M Sport Brakes with Black Calipers, Extended Shadowline Trim, and Rear Spoiler add a touch of sportiness to the 7 Series' elegant design, while the 18-speaker Bowers & Wilkins Surround Sound system and Heads-Up Display elevate your driving experience.

Whether you are interested in learning more about our team or are ready to begin shopping with us, we invite you to visit our showroom today. Conveniently located on Manchester Road just west of Hwy 141 in Manchester, MO, our team looks forward to helping you experience new levels of affordable luxury.

*See dealer for details. **Note: We utilize Market Based Pricing for all pre-owned vehicles on our lot. This ensures you have the most competitive price in the market based on mileage, equipment, and features. Utilizing this approach, our prices may fluctuate during the day on our website and may not match what is currently on 3rd party sites as they only update every 24 hours. All sale prices and discounts listed above, include all available factory incentives, discounts and rebates. Special rates must finance through BMW Financial. These are subject to change at any time.TIBBFX.

Experience the epitome of luxury and performance with this exquisite 2025 BMW 7 Series 740i xDrive. This stunning vehicle is a testament to BMW's commitment to engineering excellence, offering a captivating blend of power, technology, and refined sophistication.

Boasting a bold and commanding presence, this 7 Series is outfitted with a suite of premium features that cater to the discerning driver. Highlights include:

• BMW Individual Composition
• Driving Assistance Professional Package
• Premium Package
• M Sport Package Pro
• 18-Speaker Bowers & Wilkins Surround Sound
• Connected Package Pro
• Adaptive Suspension
• Heads-Up Display
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Heated Front and Rear Seats
• Parking Assistant Professional

Powered by a potent 3.0L I6 DOHC 24V TwinPower Turbo engine, this 740i xDrive delivers an exhilarating driving experience with its seamless 8-Speed Automatic Sport transmission and intelligent All-Wheel Drive system. With an impressive EPA-estimated 24 city/31 highway MPG, this BMW offers exceptional efficiency without compromising performance.

Step inside the cabin and be enveloped in the epitome of luxury. The BMW Individual Interior with Exclusive Contents features meticulously crafted Alcantara upholstery, complemented by stunning Carbon Fiber trim with Silver Thread and Piano Black accents. The attention to detail is simply breathtaking.

The Driving Assistance Professional Package takes this 7 Series to new heights, offering advanced driver-assist technologies like Highway Assistant, Active Driving Assistant Pro, and Surround View with 3D View. These cutting-edge features not only enhance your driving experience but also provide an unparalleled level of safety and confidence on the road.

Elevate your driving experience with the BMW Premium Package, which includes features like Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop & Go, Parking Assistant Professional, and a Drive Recorder, ensuring a seamless and effortless journey.

This 2025 BMW 7 Series 740i xDrive is a true masterpiece, blending uncompromising performance, impeccable craftsmanship, and the latest in automotive technology. Experience the difference that a BMW can make in your life. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this exceptional vehicle deserves a place in your garage.

Thank you for choosing Classic Honda, this Uyuni White 2025 Genesis G90 e-SC is a great choice! Check out the following: No Accidents! One Owner! BLACK/BORDEAUX BROWN, NAPPA LEATHER SEATING SURFACES This G90 has the following features: Convenience
  • Remote parking - Fit in anywhere! Remote parking system allows you to pull into or out of a space without having to be in the vehicle, simply use the remote control! It's perfect when the cars next to you are too close for you to be able open your doors. With remote parking, any spot is an open spot!
  • GPS linked cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until GPS linked cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed and the system uses GPS navigation data to maintain that speed without driver intervention - including slowing down for curves and anticipating hills. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, GPS linked cruise control.
Safety and Security
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control with lane change - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control with lane change, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up, and helps you make lane changes. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, hands-on cruise control with lane change.
Technology and Telematics
  • Wireless Apple CarPlay & Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring

Experience the pinnacle of performance and luxury in the 2018 Porsche Panamera Sport Turismo Turbo. This stunning silver sports car boasts a powerful V8 engine, lightning-fast 8-speed PDK transmission, and advanced all-wheel drive, delivering an exhilarating driving experience like no other.

• 4WD/AWD
• Carbon Fiber Interior Package
• Memory Package
• Sport Chrono Package

Designed to turn heads and thrill the senses, the Panamera Sport Turismo Turbo is a true masterpiece of engineering. Its sleek, aerodynamic silhouette is complemented by a host of premium features, including a panoramic sunroof, power liftgate, and 14-way power-adjustable seats with memory function.

Inside, you'll be surrounded by the finest materials and craftsmanship, with a Porsche Communication Management system, 14-speaker audio, and dual-zone climate control to keep you comfortable and connected. The adaptive suspension and 4-wheel disc brakes with ABS ensure exceptional handling and control, while the comprehensive safety suite, including airbags, traction control, and electronic stability control, provides peace of mind.

This Panamera Sport Turismo Turbo is the perfect blend of power, style, and sophistication. Whether you're carving through twisty roads or cruising in comfort, this Porsche delivers an unparalleled driving experience that will leave you wanting more.

Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional vehicle. Schedule a test drive today and experience the thrill of Porsche performance for yourself.

Experience the future of luxury performance with this exceptional 2020 Porsche Taycan Turbo. With its stunning design, thrilling driving dynamics, and cutting-edge technology, this electric sports car is the ultimate expression of Porsche's commitment to innovation and excellence.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2020 Porsche Panamera GTS. Boasting a powerful V8 engine, advanced all-wheel drive, and a sleek black exterior, this Panamera is a true expression of Porsche's renowned craftsmanship and performance.

• Complimentary 1 Year Pre-Paid Maintenance

The Panamera GTS is more than just a luxury sedan, it's a testament to Porsche's engineering excellence. With its 8-speed Porsche Doppelkupplung (PDK) transmission, you'll enjoy lightning-fast gear changes and seamless power delivery, allowing you to effortlessly conquer the open road. The all-wheel drive system provides exceptional traction and stability, ensuring a thrilling and confident driving experience in all conditions.

Step inside the Panamera GTS, and you'll be greeted by a cabin that exudes sophistication and attention to detail. The 18-way adaptive sport seats offer unparalleled comfort and support, while the Porsche Communication Management system provides intuitive control over the vehicle's advanced features. The power moonroof and liftgate add a touch of convenience and versatility, making this Panamera a true all-around performer.

Underneath the sleek black exterior lies a heart that beats with passion. The powerful V8 engine delivers an exhilarating driving experience, with ample power on tap to satisfy your need for speed. And with the impressive fuel efficiency of 16 city/23 highway MPG, you can enjoy your driving pleasure without constant trips to the gas station.

At our dealership, we take great pride in offering our customers the finest pre-owned vehicles on the market. This 2020 Porsche Panamera GTS is a testament to our commitment to excellence, and we invite you to experience its unparalleled performance and sophistication for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the true meaning of driving pleasure.

Why BUY from Paul Miller Porsche? When you choose this Graphite Grey Metallic 2021 Mercedes-Benz S-Class S 580 with 37,605 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! What this vehicle includes: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control with lane change - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control with lane change, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up, and helps you make lane changes. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, hands-on cruise control with lane change.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring

Smart device integration lets you mirror your phone wirelessly so music, navigation and messaging are available without cables, keeping the cabin connected while you focus on the road.

Forward collision mitigation continuously monitors traffic ahead and prepares or intervenes to help prevent or lessen frontal impacts, giving you extra assurance in busy driving conditions.

Pedestrian impact prevention watches for people near the roadway and can take steps to avoid collisions, improving safety around crosswalks and in crowded urban areas.

An onboard mobile hotspot provides in-car Wi‑Fi so passengers can stream, work, or stay connected on the go without using their phone data.

The rear camera gives a clear view behind the car to simplify parking and reversing by revealing obstacles you might not see from the driver’s seat.

Lane departure prevention helps keep the car centered by detecting unintended drift and applying corrective action, reducing the chance of lane-related incidents.

Rear collision mitigation monitors the area behind the vehicle and activates protective measures if a rear impact becomes likely, helping to better protect occupants.

The head-up display projects essential driving information onto the windshield so you can check speed and engine data without taking your eyes off the road.

Brake assist senses panic braking and applies maximum available braking force to help stop quickly in emergency situations

Experience the Thrill of Driving with the 2024 Cadillac CT5 V-Series: Power, Precision, and Prestige in a Coastal Blue Metallic Masterpiece
Step into the world of luxury performance with the 2024 Cadillac CT5 V-Series, a used vehicle that redefines driving pleasure. Its 3.0L V6 engine, paired with a turbocharged powertrain and 10-speed automatic transmission, delivers a seamless blend of power and precision, making every journey exhilarating. The Coastal Blue Metallic exterior is a statement of elegance, ensuring you stand out on the road.
Inside, the CT5 V-Series offers an immersive experience with a premium sound system and smart device integration, keeping you connected and entertained. Adaptive Cruise Control and a suite of advanced safety features, including Blind Spot Monitor and Lane Keeping Assist, provide peace of mind on every drive. The luxurious interior boasts power-adjustable bucket seats with lumbar support and seat memory, ensuring personalized comfort for both driver and passengers.
With its active suspension and performance tires, the CT5 V-Series offers a smooth, responsive ride, while the aluminum wheels and rear spoiler add a touch of sporty sophistication. Discover the perfect harmony of luxury and performance in this exceptional sedan, designed for those who demand more from their driving experience.

Whether you're seeking a dynamic daily driver or a prestigious long-distance cruiser, this 2024 BMW 7 Series 740i is the embodiment of refined power and sophistication. Backed by the renowned BMW Certified Pre-Owned program, this 5 Series comes with a comprehensive warranty, roadside assistance, and a multipoint inspection, ensuring peace of mind and confidence in your purchase. For over 50 illustrious years, Motor Werks has been Driven By You, dedicated to surpassing expectations and defining excellence.

Why BUY from BMW of Darien? When you choose this Black Sapphire Metallic 2022 BMW 8 Series M850i with 38,480 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! What this vehicle includes: Comfort Seating Package ($850 value)
  • Power Rear Sunshade and Rear Side Window Shades
  • Front and Rear Heated Seats
Driving Assistance Package ($100 value)
  • Active Driving Assistant
  • Parking Assistant Plus
  • Drive Recorder
  • Active Blind Spot Detection
  • Active Park Distance Control
  • Rear View Camera
  • Surround View with 3D View
Driving Assistance Professional Package ($1,700 value)
  • Extended Traffic Jam Assistant
  • Active Driving Assistant Pro
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-off cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now with hands-off cruise control simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles with minimal steering input from you. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-off cruise control.
  • Extended Traffic Jam Assistant hands-on cruise control with lane change
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay Compatibility smart device wireless mirroring

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2022 Dodge Charger R/T Scat Pack Widebody. This high-performance sedan boasts a commanding presence on the road, combining exhilarating power, advanced technology, and refined style.

Highlighted features include:
• Quick Order Package 21V Scat Pack Widebody

The Plus Group further elevates your comfort and convenience with a power tilt/telescoping steering column, blind spot monitoring, and more.

This Charger R/T Scat Pack Widebody is the perfect blend of power, style, and technology. Whether you're seeking an exhilarating daily driver or a head-turning weekend warrior, this Dodge is sure to exceed your expectations. Schedule a test drive today and experience the thrill of true American muscle.

description: The 2022 Mercedes-Benz AMG E 53 4MATIC is a masterfully balanced performance sedan that epitomizes the sweet spot of the E-Class lineup, offering a sophisticated blend of executive luxury and athletic precision. At its heart lies an innovative 3.0L turbocharged inline-six engine enhanced by an electric auxiliary compressor and the 48-volt EQ Boost system, producing a seamless 429 horsepower and 384 lb-ft of torque. This electrified powertrain enables a swift 0 60 mph sprint in just 4.4 seconds, while the AMG SPEEDSHIFT TCT 9-speed transmission and fully variable 4MATIC+ all-wheel drive ensure power is delivered with exceptional composure. Inside, the cabin is a showcase of high-end craftsmanship, featuring the dual 12.3-inch widescreen cockpit, MBUX infotainment with augmented reality navigation, and premium materials that create an atmosphere of modern opulence. Whether utilizing the AMG RIDE CONTROL+ air suspension to smooth out a long-distance cruise or engaging Sport+ mode for spirited handling, the E 53 provides a versatile and exhilarating driving experience that is as refined as it is potent.

Prestige Package ($7,200 value)
  • Driver Assistance Package

  • Head-Up Display

  • Dual Pane Acoustic Side Windows

Performance Package ($6,000 value)
  • Black-Optic Exterior Kit
  • E-Torque Vectoring Plus
  • Exterior Mirror Housings in Black Optic

  • Matte Carbon Atlas Inlays
  • HD Matrix-Design LED Headlights

Full Leather Interior ($4,000 value)
  • RS 3-Spoke Heated Multifunction Steering Wheel
  • Full Leather Interior Package
  • Ventilated Front RS Sport Seats Plus
  • Perforated Fine Nappa Leather Seating Surfaces
Convenience
  • GPS linked cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until GPS linked cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed and the system uses GPS navigation data to maintain that speed without driver intervention - including slowing down for curves and anticipating hills. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, GPS linked cruise control.
Safety and Security
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Audi smartphone interface (Apple CarPlay/Android Auto) smart device wireless mirroring

description: Black, Daytona Logo Nappa/Alcantara Seat, Daytona Edition Group, Engine: 6.4L V8 Srt Hemi Mds, Front License Plate Bracket, Granite Pearlcoat, Power Sunroof, Quick Order Package 21W Scat Pack, Tires: 275/40Zr20 As Performance, Transmission: 8-Speed Automatic (8Hp70), Wheels: 20'' X 9.5'' Forged/Painted Aluminum. This is the muscle sedan enthusiasts dream about—brutally powerful, unmistakably bold, and barely broken in. With just 1,429 original miles, this 2022 Dodge Charger Scat Pack Daytona is a rare opportunity to own a near-new example of one of the last great naturally aspirated V8 performance sedans. Finished in menacing Granite Pearlcoat over a Black interior, it delivers classic American muscle with modern performance engineering and unmistakable Daytona heritage. At its heart roars the legendary 6.4L HEMI® V8, producing 485 horsepower and 475 lb-ft of torque, paired with Dodge’s lightning-quick 8-speed TorqueFlite automatic transmission. Every throttle input is met with instant response, thunderous sound, and relentless acceleration—this is a car that stirs the soul every time you press the start button. Scat Pack Performance 6.4L HEMI® V8 – 485 HP / 475 lb-ft of torque 8-speed TorqueFlite automatic transmission with paddle shifters Launch Control and Drive Modes for customizable performance Performance-tuned suspension engineered for aggressive handling Brembo® high-performance braking system for confident stopping power This Charger isn’t just fast—it’s engineered to dominate straightaways while remaining composed through corners. Daytona Edition Group – Heritage Meets Aggression The Daytona Edition Group transforms the Scat Pack into a tribute to Dodge’s racing legacy: Daytona-specific exterior graphics and badging Gloss Black performance accents that amplify its aggressive stance Daytona interior details celebrating iconic muscle-car heritage It’s a bold visual statement that signals this Charger is something special before the engine even fires. Quick Order Package The Quick Order Package enhances convenience and performance-focused features, delivering a well-balanced blend of comfort, technology, and muscle-car attitude designed to elevate every drive. Power Sunroof Open the cabin to fresh air and sunlight at the touch of a button, adding another layer of excitement whether cruising the boulevard or heading out on an open highway. Interior – Driver-Focused and Purposeful Deeply bolstered Black performance seating Flat-bottom steering wheel for a race-inspired feel Performance Pages and digital driver displays providing real-time power, torque, and G-force data Premium materials and thoughtful ergonomics throughout Exterior – Subtle, Sinister, Iconic Granite Pearlcoat delivers a refined yet intimidating presence Widebody-inspired stance and muscular body lines Signature Scat Pack and Daytona details that demand respect The Verdict With just 1,429 miles, this 2022 Dodge Charger Scat Pack Daytona is as close to new as it gets—an increasingly rare chance to own a naturally aspirated 6.4L HEMI V8 sedan with iconic Daytona styling, modern technology, and everyday practicality.. description:
Mercedes-Benz of Palm Springs is delighted to showcase, this Certified Pre-Owned 2022 Mercedes-Benz E 450 4MATIC Sedan. Dressed in an elegant Obsidian Black Metallic exterior and featuring a refined Neva White/Magma Grey Leather interior, with just 18,082 miles, this exceptional sedan perfectly balances luxury, performance, and advanced technology.

The E-Class Sedan is a benchmark in its segment, and this E 450 4MATIC is no exception. Its Obsidian Black Metallic finish highlights the vehicles sculpted lines, while the AMG Body Styling, Night Package, and 19-inch AMG Twin 5-Spoke Wheels give it a confident and athletic presence. The Panorama Sunroof fills the cabin with natural light, and MULTIBEAM LED Headlamps ensure exceptional visibility with cutting-edge design and function.


Step inside and you are greeted by a cabin that exemplifies Mercedes-Benz craftsmanship. The Neva White/Magma Grey leather interior is complemented by Natural Grain Black Ash Wood Trim, a Nappa Leather Steering Wheel, and Multi-Color Ambient Lighting that sets the perfect mood for every drive. Advanced comfort features such as Heated & Ventilated Front Seats, KEYLESS-GO, and the intuitive MBUX Multimedia System elevate every journey, whether its a daily commute or a long-distance escape.

Engine and Performance: Powering this luxury sedan is a responsive 3.0-liter turbocharged inline-6 engine with EQ Boost, producing 362 horsepower and 369 lb-ft of torque. Paired with the refined 9G-TRONIC 9-speed automatic transmission and confident 4MATIC all-wheel drive, the E 450 delivers smooth, commanding performance with impressive efficiency and poise. The DYNAMIC SELECT system allows you to tailor the driving experience to your preferences with ease.

Key Features:

• Driver Assistance Package: Includes Active Distance Assist DISTRONIC, Active Steering Assist, Active Lane Change Assist, and advanced PRE-SAFE technologies for added confidence on every drive.

• Premium Package Lite: Enhances comfort and convenience with Surround View Camera, Burmester Surround Sound System, PARKTRONIC with Active Parking Assist, and SiriusXM Radio.

• Night Package: Adds striking black exterior accents for a sportier, more aggressive appearance.

• MULTIBEAM LED Headlamps: Intelligent lighting technology that adapts to road conditions for superior visibility.

• Panorama Sunroof: Creates an open, airy cabin experience with expansive glass and power tilt/slide functionality.

• Burmester Surround Sound System: Delivers rich, immersive audio quality throughout the cabin.

This Certified Pre-Owned 2022 Mercedes-Benz E 450 4MATIC Sedan represents a remarkable opportunity to experience timeless luxury, advanced safety, and refined performance. Available now at Mercedes-Benz of Palm Springs, this E-Class is ready to elevate every drive with sophistication and confidence.



Mercedes-Benz of Palm Springs is a member of the indiGO Auto Group. Our dealership features a beautiful showroom, fully staffed factory certified service center, parts department, finance department, detail department, and accessories boutique. Allow us to also help arrange transportation of your new car directly to your home anywhere in the world. Trade-in proposals are always welcome. If you like this vehicle and have questions, simply call, email, or drop by our location. We invite you to Activate Your Ownership with us today!

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2022 Mercedes-Benz S-Class S 500 4MATIC®. Crafted with the utmost precision and attention to detail, this luxury sedan is a true masterpiece of German engineering.

Boasting a sleek and sophisticated exterior in a captivating Gray hue, this S-Class is powered by a 3.0L V6 Turbocharged engine paired with a 9-Speed Automatic transmission and the renowned 4MATIC® all-wheel-drive system. With an impressive fuel efficiency of 21 MPG in the city and 30 MPG on the highway, this vehicle combines power and efficiency to deliver an unparalleled driving experience.

Key features of this remarkable S-Class include:

• Navigation System
• 15 Speakers
• Burmester® 3D Surround Sound System
• Premium audio system: MBUX
• Adaptive suspension
• Auto-leveling suspension
• Panorama Power Moonroof
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Leather Upholstery
• 19" 5-Multi Spoke Alloy Wheels

Designed to elevate your senses and provide the ultimate in luxury, comfort, and technology, this 2022 Mercedes-Benz S-Class S 500 4MATIC® is a true masterpiece on the road. Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence and let this stunning sedan transform your daily commute into a captivating journey.

Imagine yourself behind the wheel, surrounded by the finest materials and the latest advancements in automotive technology. The MBUX infotainment system with its intuitive touchscreen interface and the Burmester® 3D Surround Sound System will immerse you in a world of entertainment and convenience. The adaptive suspension and auto-leveling features ensure a smooth and composed ride, while the 4MATIC® all-wheel-drive system provides exceptional traction and stability in any driving condition.

Stepping inside the cabin, you'll be greeted by the luxurious leather upholstery and the thoughtfully designed ergonomics that prioritize both style and comfort. The heated and ventilated front seats, along with the panoramic power moonroof, create an oasis of relaxation and refinement.

This 2022 Mercedes-Benz S-Class S 500 4MATIC® is more than just a vehicle – it's a statement of sophistication and an embodiment of the brand's relentless pursuit of excellence. Experience the pinnacle of automotive luxury and schedule a test drive today. Let this exceptional sedan transform the way you think about driving.

Why BUY from BMW of Lafayette? When you choose this Individual Dravit Grey Metallic 2022 BMW 8 Series M850i with 26,253 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! What this vehicle includes: Driving Assistance Package ($100 value)
  • Active Driving Assistant
  • Parking Assistant Plus
  • Drive Recorder
  • Active Blind Spot Detection
  • Active Park Distance Control
  • Rear View Camera
  • Surround View with 3D View
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay Compatibility smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
Come on in to BMW of Lafayette today at 178 Sagamore Parkway South Lafayette IN 47905 or call to schedule a test drive!

description: 2022 Lucid Air Grand TouringClean Carfax!DreamDrive Pro w/LIDAR AWD w/Dual Permanent-Magnet Motors 900-Volt Charging System Stellar White Metallic Paint inchMojaveinch Black & Graphite Upholstery 21inch Aero Blade Alloy Wheels Glass Canopy Roof Heated & Vented Front Seats w/Massage Heated Rear Seats 34inch Glass Cockpit Display Surreal Sound Audio SystemThis 2022 Lucid Air was ordered with the Grand Touring trim level that features an all-wheel-drive powertrain with dual motors, a 112.0-kWh battery pack, and a 900-volt charging system. Finished in Stellar White Metallic over a Mojave-scheme black interior, it has a glass-canopy roof, adaptive damping, 21″ Aero Blade wheels, heated and ventilated front seats, heated rear seats, a Surreal Sound audio system, a 34″ Glass Cockpit display, and a DreamDrive Pro driver assistance program with LIDAR. The body’s white finish is contrasted by Platinum Polish roof trim, and the car has Intelligent Micro Lens Array LED headlights, soft-close doors, retracting illuminated door handles, a power-operated charging door and trunk lids, and Speedform LED taillights. Its 900-volt charging system has a Wunderbox onboard boost charger, and Lucid states that up to 300 miles of range can be added in 21 minutes at a 350 kW DC fast charger. Powered by a 112-kWh battery pack, the dual AC permanent-magnet synchronous electric motors drive all four of the 21″ Aero Blade alloy wheels, which are mounted with 245/35 front and 265/35 rear Pirelli P Zero Elect tires. The powertrain was rated at 819 horsepower and 885 lb-ft of torque when new, and EPA-estimated range with 21″ wheels was rated at 469 miles.Equipped with heating, ventilation, and massage functions, the 20-way power-adjustable front seats are trimmed in Lucid Black and Graphite leather, while Carbon Oak trim and microsuede upholstery accent the Mojave-scheme interior. Appointments include four-zone climate control, wireless charging, a 21-speaker Surreal Sound audio system, and Lucid UX infotainment.The heated leather-wrapped multifunction steering wheel fronts a 34″ Glass Cockpit display with 5k resolution. The car was built with DreamDrive hardware for semi-autonomous driving capability, and the driver is aided by LIDAR adaptive cruise control, a surround-view camera system, blind-spot monitoring, Automatic Park In & Out, Park Distance Warning, and a driver monitoring system with distracted / drowsy alerts.
